20a%20draft%20resolution%20introduced%20by%20Pakistan%20and%20co-sponsored%20by%20China%20on%20Islamophobia%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20prevalence%20of%20%E2%80%9Creligiophobia%E2%80%9D%20against%20Hinduism%2C%20Buddhism%2C%20Sikhism%20and%20other%20faiths%20facing%20violence%20and%20discrimination%20must%20also%20be%20acknowledged%20rather%20than%20singling%20out%20just%20one%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20193-member%20General%20Assembly%20adopted%20the%20resolution%20%E2%80%98Measures%20to%20combat%20Islamophobia'%2C%20introduced%20by%20Pakistan%20on%20Friday%2C%20with%20115%20nations%20voting%20in%20favour%2C%20none%20against%20and%2044%20abstentions%2C%20including%20India%2C%20Brazil%2C%20France%2C%20Germany%2C%20Italy%2C%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Permanent%20Representative%20to%20the%20UN%20Ambassador%20Ruchira%20Kamboj%20voiced%20condemnation%20of%20all%20acts%20motivated%20by%20anti-Semitism%2C%20Christianophobia%20and%20Islamophobia%20but%20asserted%20that%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20such%20phobias%20extend%20beyond%20Abrahamic%20religions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CClear%20evidence%20shows%20that%20over%20decades%2C%20followers%20of%20non-Abrahamic%20religions%20have%20also%20been%20affected%20by%20religiophobia.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20the%20emergence%20of%20contemporary%20forms%20of%20religiophobia%2C%20particularly%20anti-Hindu%2C%20anti-Buddhist%20and%20anti-Sikh%20sentiments%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20in%20an%20explanation%20of%20India's%20position%20on%20the%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20stressed%20that%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20resolution%20should%20not%20establish%20a%20precedent%20that%20could%20result%20in%20numerous%20resolutions%20centred%20on%20phobias%20tied%20to%20specific%20religions%2C%20%E2%80%9Cpotentially%20dividing%20the%20United%20Nations%20into%20religious%20camps.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20UN%20to%20maintain%20its%20stance%20above%20such%20religious%20concerns%2C%20which%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20fragment%20us%20rather%20than%20unite%20us%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20peace%20and%20harmony%2C%20embracing%20the%20world%20as%20one%20global%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kamboj%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20called%20on%20all%20member%20states%20to%20consider%20the%20broader%20scope%20of%20religious%20discrimination%20that%20persists%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20issue%20of%20Islamophobia%20is%20undoubtedly%20significant%2C%20we%20must%20acknowledge%20that%20other%20religions%20are%20also%20facing%20discrimination%20and%20violence.%20Allocating%20resources%20solely%20to%20combat%20Islamophobia%2C%20while%20neglecting%20similar%20challenges%20faced%20by%20other%20faiths%2C%20might%20inadvertently%20perpetuate%20a%20sense%20of%20exclusion%20and%20inequality%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamboj%20told%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20crucial%20to%20recognise%E2%80%9D%20that%20Hinduism%2C%20with%20over%201.2%20billion%20followers%2C%20Buddhism%20with%20more%20than%20535%20million%20and%20Sikhism%20with%20over%2030%20million%20followers%20worldwide%2C%20are%20all%20subject%20to%20religiophobia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20time%20that%20we%20acknowledge%20the%20prevalence%20of%20religiophobia%2C%20rather%20than%20single%20out%20just%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamboj%20said%20the%20contemporary%20forms%20of%20religiophobia%20are%20evident%20in%20the%20increasing%20attacks%20on%20religious%20places%20of%20worship%20such%20as%20gurudwaras%2C%20monasteries%20and%20temples%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20spreading%20of%20hatred%20and%20disinformation%20against%20non-Abrahamic%20religions%20in%20many%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20destruction%20of%20the%20Bamiyan%20Buddhas%2C%20violations%20of%20gurudwara%20premises%2C%20massacres%20of%20Sikh%20pilgrims%20in%20gurudwaras%2C%20attacks%20on%20temples%2C%20and%20the%20glorification%20of%20breaking%20idols%20in%20temples%20all%20contribute%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20contemporary%20forms%20of%20religiophobia%20against%20non-Abrahamic%20religions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20destruction%20of%20the%20giant%20Buddha%20statues%20of%20Bamiyan%20in%20Afghanistan%20by%20the%20Taliban%20in%20March%202001%20led%20to%20global%20condemnation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamboj%20underlined%20that%20India%20stands%20against%20all%20forms%20of%20religiophobia%2C%20be%20it%20antisemitism%2C%20Christianophobia%2C%20or%20Islamophobia%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20stand%20against%20all%20anti-Hindu%2C%20anti-Buddhist%2C%20and%20anti-Sikh%20sentiments.%E2%80%9D%20The%20resolution%20condemned%20the%20incitement%20to%20discrimination%2C%20hostility%20or%20violence%20against%20Muslims%20as%20manifested%20in%20the%20increasing%20number%20of%20incidents%20of%20desecration%20of%20their%20holy%20book%2C%20attacks%20on%20mosques%2C%20sites%20and%20shrines%20and%20other%20acts%20of%20religious%20intolerance%2C%20negative%20stereotyping%2C%20hatred%20and%20violence%20against%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20requested%20UN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20to%20appoint%20a%20United%20Nations%20Special%20Envoy%20to%20combat%20Islamophobia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20said%20it%20%E2%80%9Cin%20principle%E2%80%9D%20is%20opposed%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20post%20of%20a%20Special%20Envoy%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20single%20religion%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamboj%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20substantial%20budgetary%20implications%20of%20establishing%20such%20a%20position%20%E2%80%9Cprompt%20us%20to%20pause%20and%20reflect%20on%20whether%20this%20is%20the%20most%20effective%20use%20of%20resources.%20Could%20we%20not%20achieve%20greater%20impact%20through%20a%20more%20inclusive%20approach%20that%20addresses%20religious%20discrimination%20in%20its%20entirety%3F%E2%80%9D%20She%20underscored%20that%20India's%20rich%20history%20as%20a%20pluralistic%20and%20democratic%20nation%2C%20embracing%20diverse%20religions%2C%20has%20long%20served%20as%20a%20refuge%20for%20those%20persecuted%20for%20their%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhether%20Zoroastrians%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Jews%2C%20or%20adherents%20of%20any%20other%20belief%2C%20they%20have%20consistently%20found%20in%20India%20a%20sanctuary%20free%20from%20persecution%20or%20discrimination%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20adopting%20the%20resolution%2C%20the%20Assembly%20rejected%20two%20amendments%20to%20the%20draft%20introduced%20by%20Belgium%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20EU.%20India%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20both%20the%20amendments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20amendment%20proposed%20changes%20in%20the%20resolution's%20language%20to%20remove%20references%20to%20the%20desecration%20of%20the%20Quran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20amendment%20would%20have%20called%20for%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9CUnited%20Nations%20focal%20point%2C%20within%20existing%20structures%20and%20resources%2C%20to%20combat%20anti-Muslim%20discrimination%E2%80%9D%20instead%20of%20a%20UN%20special%20envoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20General%20Assembly%20adopted%20a%20resolution%20in%202022%20proclaiming%20March%2015%20as%20the%20International%20Day%20to%20Combat%20Islamophobia%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%202019%20mass%20shootings%20in%20two%20mosques%20in%20Christchurch%2C%20New%20Zealand%20that%20had%20killed%20over%2050%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20remarks%20to%20mark%20the%20day%2C%20Guterres%20said%20that%20around%20the%20world%2C%20there%20is%20a%20rising%20tide%20of%20anti-Muslim%20hate%20and%20bigotry%20in%20many%20forms%20such%20as%20structural%20and%20systemic%20discrimination%2C%20unequal%20immigration%20policies%2C%20unwarranted%20surveillance%20and%20profiling%20and%20restrictions%20in%20accessing%20citizenship%2C%20education%2C%20employment%20and%20justice.%