20is%20the%20issue%20for%20him%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20batting%20will%20ever%20be%20an%20issue%20for%20him.%20I%20think%20it's%20the%20wicketkeeping.%20The%20knees%20are%20getting%20worn%20out%20and%20he%20loves%20keeping.%20So%2C%20because%20he%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20stand%20there%20and%20add%20value%2C%20he'll%20probably%20move%20on%20from%20the%20game%20than%20for%20any%20other%20reason%2C%26quot%3B%20Uthappa%20said%20on%20Jio%20Cinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20England%20and%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Eoin%20Morgan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F833-eoin-morgan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EEoin%20Morgan%3C%2Fa%3E%20echoed%20Uthappa's%20sentiments%2C%20saying%20that%20time%20is%20not%20on%20Dhoni's%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20the%20type%20of%20guy%20that%20writes%20his%20own%20script.%20It's%20a%20feeling%20thing%2C%20most%20likely%20for%20him.%20If%20his%20knees%20are%20as%20bad%20as%20Robbie%20eludes%2C%20time%20is%20probably%20ticking%20because%20he%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20outstay%20the%20position%20that%20he%20has%20put%20the%20franchise%20in%20simply%20because%20he'll%20always%20want%20the%20franchise%20to%20succeed.%20He's%20so%20generous%20with%20his%20time%2C%20with%20his%20respect%2C%20he'll%20want%20somebody%20to%20come%20in%20and%20take%20over%20the%20mantle%2C%26quot%3B%20Morgan%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhoni%20had%20flown%20to%20Mumbai%20from%20Ahmedabad%20after%20the%20final%20last%20year%20and%20consulted%20renowned%20sports%20orthopaedic%20surgeon%20Dr%20Dinshaw%20Pardiwala%2C%20who%20is%20also%20on%20the%20BCCI%20medical%20panel%20and%20had%20performed%20surgeries%20on%20a%20number%20of%20top%20Indian%20cricketers%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rishabh%20Pant%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107048-rishabh-pant-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERishabh%20Pant%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20successfully%20underwent%20a%20left%20knee%20surgery%2C%20and%20has%20been%20declared%20fit%20to%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710565140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4rd70g9g_ms-dhoni-csk-bcci_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fon-ex-csk-stars-ms-dhoni-wont-be-able-add-value-comment-eoin-morgans-time-ticking-bombshell-5248521%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20has%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20speculation%20that%20IPL%202024%20is%20going%20to%20be%20MS%20Dhoni's%20last.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Murder%20Mubarak%20Is%20Watchable%20All%20The%20Way%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20before%20election%20day%20at%20an%20upscale%20Delhi%20club%2C%20the%20members%20are%20rattled%20by%20the%20death%20of%20a%20brawny%20Zumba%20trainer.%20The%20incident%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20dismissed%20as%20a%20gym%20accident.%20But%20a%20seasoned%20police%20investigator%2C%20employing%20unconventional%20methods%2C%20sniffs%20foul%20play%20and%20decides%20that%20there%20is%20more%20here%20than%20meets%20the%20eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20how%20%3Ci%3EMurder%20Mubarak%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20a%20whodunnit%20with%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20caper%20film%2C%20opens.%20Crisply%20edited%20and%20studded%20with%20performances%20that%20by%20and%20large%20are%20in%20perfect%20sync%20with%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20genre%2C%20it%20is%20watchable%20all%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Assistant%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20Bhavani%20Singh%20(Pankaj%20Tripathi)%20ferrets%20around%20for%20clues%20and%20conclusions%2C%20the%20Homi%20Adajania-directed%20murder%20mystery%20wends%20its%20way%20through%20unusual%20and%20therefore%20unpredictable%20twists%20and%20turns%20that%20keep%20the%20Netflix%20film%20on%20a%20sustained%20boil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%20the%20end%2C%20the%20cop%20describes%20what%20we%20have%20just%20seen%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpeculiar%26quot%3B%20love%20story.%20It%20indeed%20is.%20Murder%20Mubarak%20is%20not%20only%20about%20a%20romantic%20liaison%20between%20two%20people%20but%20also%20about%20an%20affair%20that%20a%20collective%20of%20people%20has%20with%20a%20swish%20club%20where%20they%20descend%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20momentarily%20wishing%20away%2C%20if%20not%20actually%20washing%20away%2C%20their%20problems%20and%20peccadilloes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20another%20point%20in%20his%20investigation%2C%20Bhavani%20asserts%20that%20a%20killer%20is%20usually%20an%20ordinary%20person.%20He%20(or%20she)%2C%20the%20policeman%20says%2C%20is%20in%20all%20likelihood%20a%20club%20member%20who%20is%20right%20now%20congratulating%20himself%20(or%20herself)%20for%20getting%20away%20with%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdapted%20for%20the%20screen%20by%20Gazal%20Dhaliwal%20and%20Suprotim%20Sengupta%20from%20Anuja%20Chauhan's%20Club%20You%20to%20Death%2C%20Murder%20Mubarak%20presents%20a%20gallery%20comprising%20bigmouths%2C%20hunks%2C%20voyeurs%2C%20socialites%2C%20predators%20and%20lovers%2C%20each%20of%20whom%20is%20on%20Bhavani's%20list%20of%20suspects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guy%20who%20dies%2C%20Leo%20Matthews%20(Aashim%20Gulati)%2C%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20gave%20nearly%20everyone%20he%20dealt%20with%20a%20reason%20to%20want%20him%20dead.%20Bhavani's%20job%20isn't%20easy%2C%20but%20he%20makes%20it%20look%20like%20a%20walk%20in%20the%20park%20as%20he%2C%20with%20an%20able%20assistant%2C%20Sub-Inspector%20Padam%20Kumar%20(Priyank%20Tiwari)%2C%20lays%20one%20trap%20at%20a%20time%20and%20waits%20for%20the%20killer%20to%20walk%20into%20it%20and%20expose%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhavani%20is%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20other%20Hindi%20movie%20sleuths.%20He%20prefers%20not%20to%20don%20a%20uniform.%20He%20does%20not%20even%20carry%20a%20gun.%20The%20unflappable%2048-year-old%20man%20has%20a%20faint%2C%20all-knowing%20smile%20on%20his%20lips%20when%20he%20reacts%20to%20provocation%20and%20stonewalling%20with%20gentle%20repartee.%20He%20is%20only%20ten%20days%20away%20from%20relocating%20to%20Lucknow.%20His%20wife%20has%20had%20enough%20of%20the%20grime%20and%20slime%20of%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaced%20with%20sly%20humour%20directed%20against%20privilege%2C%20vanity%20and%20the%20hollow%20bubble%20that%20Royal%20Delhi%20Club%20represents%2C%20the%20story%20borrows%20methodologies%20familiar%20to%20detective%20genre%20fans%20to%20deliver%20a%20commentary%20on%20a%20status-conscious%20class%20desperate%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20what%20they%20believe%20to%20be%20their%20birthright.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhavani%20receives%20unsolicited%20help%20from%20a%20young%20widow%20Bambi%20Todi%20(Sara%20Ali%20Khan)%20and%20an%20activist-lawyer%20Akash%20%26quot%3BKashi%26quot%3B%20Dogra%20(Vijay%20Varma)%2C%20lovers%20who%20parted%20ways%20years%20ago%20for%20reasons%20unknown.%20The%20latter%20is%20in%20Delhi%20for%20Diwali.%20He%20has%20lived%20in%20Kolkata%20for%20three%20years%2C%20a%20period%20during%20which%2C%20his%20mother%20(Grusha%20Kapoor)%20believes%2C%20the%20man%20picked%20up%20his%20%26quot%3BCommie%26quot%3B%20tendencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20needle%20of%20suspicion%20moves%20one%20way%2C%20then%20another%2C%20and%20then%20yet%20another.%20Bhavani%20spares%20nobody.%20On%20his%20widening%20radar%20is%20Cookie%20Katoch%20(Dimple%20Kapadia)%2C%20known%20for%20her%20tequila%20and%20beetroot%20cocktail%3B%20Roshni%20Batra%20(Tisca%20Chopra)%20and%20her%20son%20Yash%20Batra%20(Suhail%20Nayyar)%2C%20a%20drug%20addict%20just%20out%20of%20rehab%3B%20and%20Shehnaz%20Noorani%20(Karisma%20Kapoor)%2C%20a%20fading%20movie%20actress%20who%20throws%20her%20hat%20in%20the%20ring%20for%20the%20post%20of%20club%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShehnaz's%20rival%20is%20Rannvijay%20Singh%20(Sanjay%20Kapoor)%2C%20a%20man%20from%20a%20royal%20family%20who%20never%20lets%20anybody%20forget%20his%20lineage.%20He%20is%20at%20home%20in%20a%20club%20where%20ayahs%2C%20servants%2C%20gunmen%20and%20security%20guards%20are%20not%20allowed%20beyond%20a%20point%20and%20employees%20and%20waiters%20are%20barred%20from%20using%20restrooms%20meant%20for%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FvBQcU00U9O0%3Fsi%3De_RnFyv_SwaPj9f-%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20staff%20at%20Royal%20Delhi%20Club%20-%20where%2C%20the%20outgoing%20president%20Devendra%20Bhatti%20(Deven%20Bhojani)%20tells%20Bhavani%2C%20heads%20of%20state%20have%20played%20golf%20-%20have%20their%20own%20ways%20of%20getting%20back%20at%20the%20ill-behaved%20members.%20One%20of%20the%20club's%20oldest%20staffers%20-%20Guppie%20Ram%20(Brijendra%20Kala)%20-%20has%20lost%20his%20mind%20but%20knows%20enough%20to%20be%20of%20use%20to%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20there%20is%20Ganga%20(Tara%20Alisha%20Berry)%20who%20works%20in%20the%20club's%20beauty%20parlour.%20Her%20back%20story%20begins%20to%20have%20a%20bearing%20on%20the%20investigation%20as%20Bhavani%20inches%20ever%20closer%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20truth.%20What%20complicates%20the%20probe%20is%20that%20while%20the%20killer%20could%20be%20anybody%20who%20has%20ever%20had%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20the%20victim%2C%20none%20of%20the%20suspects%20is%20outright%20wicked.%20They%20do%20not%20look%20like%20folks%20who%20would%20use%20murder%20as%20a%20weapon%20against%20anybody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20with%20which%20Murder%20Mubarak%20kicks%20off%20isn't%20the%20only%20one%20that%20occurs%20in%20the%20film.%20There%20are%20three%20others%20along%20the%20way%20-%20a%20murder%20committed%20in%20the%20past%2C%20a%20suspected%20suicide%20in%20the%20present%2C%20and%20a%20tragic%20accident%20involving%20a%20pet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20is%20set%20in%20a%20world%20where%20darkness%20of%20the%20soul%20dominates%20but%20director%20of%20photography%20Linesh%20Desai%20does%20not%20smother%20it%20with%20overly%20atmospheric%20lighting.%20Much%20of%20Murder%20Mubarak%20plays%20out%20in%20open%20spaces%20but%20the%20film%20is%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20a%20cocoon.%20Life%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20in%20the%20neighbourhoods%20of%20Delhi%20aren't%20part%20of%20the%20film's%20visual%20palette.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ci%3EMurder%20Mubarak%3C%2Fi%3E%20moves%20indoors%2C%20the%20frames%20aren't%20excessively%20gloomy%20and%20grim.%20The%20even%20lighting%20conveys%20the%20superficiality%20of%20the%20world%20that%20club%20exists%20in.%20It%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20contrast%20to%20the%20complex%2C%20twisted%20knots%20that%20Bhavani%20must%20untangle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPankaj%20Tripathi's%20effortless%20performance%20helps%20Murder%20Mubarak%20settle%20into%20a%20steady%20rhythm.%20Sara%20Ali%20Khan%20is%20a%20touch%20erratic%2C%20swaying%20awkwardly%20between%20being%20a%20seductress%20and%20turning%20into%20a%20woman%20with%20her%20share%20of%20secrets.%20Vijay%20Varma%20keeps%20it%20simple%20and%20supple%20as%20he%20plays%20a%20man%20who%20is%20ill%20at%20ease%20with%20all%20the%20ostentation%20around%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20ensemble%20cast%2C%20Dimple%20Kapadia%2C%20Karisma%20Kapoor%2C%20Tisca%20Chopra%20and%20Sanjay%20Kapoor%20play%20their%20parts%20with%20just%20the%20right%20mix%20of%20playfulness%20and%20intensity%2C%20adding%20their%20collective%20mite%20to%20the%20jigsaw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EMurder%20Mubarak%3C%2Fi%3E%20does%20not%20rely%20on%20action%20for%20effect.%20And%20the%20script%20ensures%20that%20talk%20isn't%20dull.%20The%20editing%20keeps%20pace%20with%20the%20speed%20at%20which%20the%20investigation%20unfolds%20and%20the%20directorial%20flourishes%20ensure%20that%20the%20film%20is%20never%20less%20than%20riveting.%3C%2Fp%3