0the%20fire%20may%20not%20have%20been%20accidental.%20Constable%20Taryn%20Young%20of%20Peel%20Police%20described%20the%20fire%20as%20%26quot%3Bsuspicious%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20that%20they%20are%20combing%20through%20all%20evidence%20available%20to%20ascertain%20the%20cause.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20time%2C%20we%20are%20investigating%20this%20with%20our%20homicide%20bureau%2C%20and%20we%20are%20deeming%20this%20as%20suspicious%20as%20the%20Ontario%20Fire%20Marshal%20has%20deemed%20that%20this%20fire%20was%20not%20accidental%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Young%20told%20news%20channel%20CTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fire%20engulfed%20a%20home%20at%20the%20Big%20Sky%20Way%20and%20Van%20Kirk%20Drive%20area%20of%20Brampton%20on%20March%207%2C%20a%20press%20release%20by%20the%20Peel%20Police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEyewitnesses%20reported%20hearing%20a%20loud%20explosion%20before%20the%20inferno%20engulfed%20the%20residence%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20puzzling%20circumstances%20surrounding%20the%20incident.%20Kenneth%20Yousaf%2C%20a%20neighbor%20of%20the%20deceased%20family%2C%20recounted%20the%20harrowing%20moment%20when%20he%20witnessed%20the%20house%20fully%20engulfed%20in%20flames.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fd6kj70rg_indian-origin-couple-canada_625x300_16_March_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYousaf%20said%20he%20was%20alerted%20to%20the%20fire%20last%20week%20by%20a%20family%20member%2C%20who%20heard%20a%20big%20%26quot%3Bbang.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20came%20out%2C%20the%20house%20was%20on%20fire.%20So%20sad.%20Within%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20everything%20was%20down%20to%20the%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20Yousaf%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20CTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20fire%20was%20put%20out%2C%20cops%20located%20w