nvoy-on-caa-implementation-2515415-2024-03-15%5C%22%3EIndia%20Today%20Conclave%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20the%20principle%20of%20religious%20freedom%20and%20equality%20was%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20give%20up%20on%20principles%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20close%20you%20are%20with%20friends%2C%20or%20if%20it%20comes%20from%20your%20worst%20enemy%2C%20when%20those%20are%20principles%20that%20you%20stand%20for%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20ambassador.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20invite%20you%20to%20do%20the%20same%20for%20our%20imperfect%20democracy.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20one-way%20street%2C%E2%80%9D%20Garcetti%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20same%20day%2C%20India%20rebuked%20the%20US%2C%20dismissing%20its%20expressed%20concern%20about%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20CAA%20as%20%E2%80%9Cmisinformed%E2%80%9D%20and%20implying%20that%20Washington%E2%80%99s%20criticism%20was%20allegedly%20driven%20by%20%E2%80%9Cvote%20bank%20politics.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20had%20notified%20the%20rules%20for%20implementing%20the%20CAA%2C%20which%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20parliament%20over%20four%20years%20ago.%20The%20rules%20would%20also%20allow%20minorities%20persecuted%20on%20religious%20grounds%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan%20to%20acquire%20citizenship%20in%20India%2C%20but%20it%20does%20not%20accord%20this%20privilege%20to%20Muslim%20minority%20groups%20in%20those%20countries%20like%20Ahmeddiyas%20and%20Hazaras.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20daily%20briefing%20on%20Thursday%20in%20Washington%2C%20the%20US%20state%20department%20spokesperson%20Mathew%20Miller%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%20we%20are%20concerned%20about%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20on%20March%2011.%20We%20are%20closely%20monitoring%20this%20act%20%E2%80%93%20how%20this%20act%20will%20be%20implemented.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Crespect%20for%20religious%20freedom%20and%20equal%20treatment%20under%20the%20law%20for%20all%20communities%20are%20fundamental%20democratic%20principles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Funderstanding-caa-rules-the-process-and-what-it-means-to-resist%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20CAA%20Rules%2C%20the%20Process%2C%20and%20What%20It%20Means%20to%20Resist%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20reacted%20sharply%20that%20CAA%20is%20%E2%80%9Can%20internal%20matter%20of%20India%20and%20is%20in%20keeping%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20inclusive%20traditions%20and%20our%20long-standing%20commitment%20to%20human%20rights%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20described%20the%20US%20State%20department%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20as%20%E2%80%9Cmisplaced%2C%20misinformed%2C%20and%20unwarranted%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20constitution%20guarantees%20freedom%20of%20religion%20to%20all%20its%20citizens.%20There%20are%20no%20grounds%20for%20any%20concern%20on%20treatment%20of%20minorities.%20Vote%20bank%20politics%20should%20not%20determine%20views%20about%20a%20laudable%20initiative%20to%20help%20those%20in%20distress%2C%E2%80%9D%20asserted%20Jaiswal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Clectures%20by%20those%20who%20have%20a%20limited%20understanding%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20pluralistic%20traditions%20and%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20post-partition%20history%20are%20best%20not%20attempted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPartners%20and%20well-wishers%20of%20India%20should%20welcome%20the%20intent%20with%20which%20this%20step%20has%20been%20taken%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20MEA%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20the%20CAA%20granted%20safe%20haven%20to%20%E2%80%9Cpersecuted%20minorities%20belonging%20to%20Hindu%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Buddhist%2C%20Jain%2C%20Parsi%2C%20and%20Christian%20communities%20from%20Afghanistan%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20Bangladesh%20who%20have%20entered%20India%20on%20or%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPublished%20on%20March%2015%20at%209%20pm%2C%20this%20story%20has%20been%20updated%20with%20the%20comments%20of%20Eric%20Garcetti%2C%20US%20Ambassador%20to%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710556252000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F15193046%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-15-at-7.30.15-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fafter-us-expresses-concern-over-caa-india-says-washingtons-criticism-due-to-vote-bank-politics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'You%20can't%20give%20up%20on%20principles%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20close%20you%20are%20with%20friends%2C%20or%20if%20it%20comes%20from%20your%20worst%20enemy%2C%20when%20those%20are%20principles%20that%20you%20stand%20for%2C'%20said%20the%20US%20Ambassador%20to%20India%20at%20the%20India%20Today%20Conclave.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fafter-us-expresses-concern-over-caa-india-says-washingtons-criticism-due-to-vote-bank-politics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Himanta%20Sarma%20Warns%20Congress%20MP%20Of%20Legal%20Action%20Over%20Poll%20Bonds%20Charge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAssam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20on%20Friday%20threatened%20legal%20action%20against%20Congress%20MP%20Pradyut%20Bordoloi%20over%20his%20social%20media%20posts%20alleging%20corruption%20by%20the%20BJP%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2