Dreamliner%20model%20to%20inspect%20certain%20switches%20in%20the%20cockpit%2C%20after%20a%20New%20Zealand-bound%20LATAM%20plane%20dropped%20violently%20mid-flight%2C%20injuring%20dozens%20of%20travellers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20investigation%20of%20Flight%20LA800%20is%20ongoing%20and%20we%20defer%20to%20the%20investigation%20authorities%20on%20any%20potential%20findings%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20US%20aeronautics%20giant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20taken%20the%20precautionary%20measure%20of%20reminding%20787%20operators%20of%20a%20service%20bulletin%20issued%20in%202017%20which%20included%20instructions%20for%20inspecting%20and%20maintaining%20switches%20on%20flight%20deck%20seats%2C%26quot%3B%20Boeing%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20recommending%20operators%20perform%20an%20inspection%20at%20the%20next%20maintenance%20opportunity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20regularly%20sends%20recommendations%20about%20its%20planes%20to%20its%20clients.%20But%20this%20one%20involved%20a%20particularly%20dangerous%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chilean%20airlines%20LATAM%20was%20flying%20Monday%20from%20Sydney%2C%20Australia%20to%20Auckland%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F50-injured-as-latam-flight-suddenly-loses-altitude-blood-was-on-ceiling-5217546%5C%22%3Ewhen%20the%20plane%20suddenly%20plunged%20earthward%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20flinging%20unrestrained%20passengers%20out%20of%20their%20seats%20and%20smashing%20some%20into%20the%20cabin%20roof.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifty%20people%20were%20injured%2C%20including%2013%20who%20were%20hospitalized.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20on%20Tuesday%20attributed%20the%20accident%20to%20an%20unspecified%20%26quot%3Btechnical%20event.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%20citing%20US%20industry%20sources%2C%20said%20Friday%20the%20incident%20was%20caused%20by%20the%20clumsiness%20of%20a%20crew%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20a%20flight%20attendant%20inadvertently%20hit%20a%20switch%20on%20the%20pilot's%20seat%20while%20serving%20a%20meal%2C%20causing%20a%20motorized%20feature%20to%20thrust%20the%20pilot%20into%20the%20controls%20and%20push%20the%20plane's%20nose%20sharply%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20switch%20is%20usually%20covered%20and%20is%20not%20meant%20to%20be%20used%20when%20the%20pilot%20is%20in%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContacted%20in%20Chile%20by%20AFP%2C%20LATAM%20refused%20to%20comment%2C%20citing%20the%20ongoing%20investigation.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20beginning%20we%20have%20collaborated%20with%20the%20authorities%20to%20clarify%20this%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20also%20refused%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20its%20part%2C%20the%20US%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20(FAA)%20said%20it%20was%20convening%20a%20Corrective%20Action%20Review%20Board%20(CARB)%20made%20up%20of%20safety%20experts%20to%20study%20the%20matter%20%26quot%3Band%20provide%20feedback%20to%20Boeing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20process%20will%20include%20reviewing%20the%202017%20service%20bulletin%20related%20to%20the%20switches%20in%20the%20pilot%20seats.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20has%20suffered%20a%20series%20of%20safety%20issues%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20including%20the%20fatal%20crashes%20of%20737%20MAX%20planes%20in%202018%20and%202019%20that%20killed%20more%20than%20350%20people%20and%20the%20near-catastrophic%20incident%20in%20January%20when%20a%20fuselage%20panel%20on%20a%20Boeing%20737%20MAX%209%20Alaska%20Airlines%20jet%20blew%20off%20mid-flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20a%20Boeing%20777%20jetliner%20bound%20for%20Japan%20had%20to%20make%20an%20emergency%20landing%20shortly%20after%20takeoff%20from%20San%20Francisco%20when%20a%20wheel%20fell%20off%20and%20plunged%20into%20an%20airport%2