peaking%20at%20the%20ET%20Awards%202023%20where%20he%20was%20honoured%20as%20the%20'Reformer%20of%20the%20Year'%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%20when%20the%20world%20thinks%20of%20India%2C%20the%20world%20actually%20sees%20a%20country%20which%20is%20able%20to%20seek%20its%20own%20solutions%2C%20speak%20its%20own%20mind%2C%20which%20will%20stand%20up%2C%20which%20stood%20up%20for%20our%20consumer%20interests%20when%20it%20came%20to%20its%20energy%20choices%2C%20which%20stood%20up%20for%20its%20national%20security%20when%20it%20came%20to%20deploying%20on%20our%20northern%20frontiers%20and%20in%20staying%20with%20the%20Quad.%20So%20this%20is%20a%20different%20India%20today%2C%20and%20I%20cannot%20tell%20you%20how%20proud%20I%20am%20to%20represent%20it%20abroad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20noted%20that%20India%2C%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20has%20left%20a%20deeper%20imprint%20on%20world%20consciousness.%20He%20said%20the%20world%20saw%20how%20India%20has%20tackled%20challenges%20such%20as%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20and%20shipped%20vaccines%20and%20other%20life-saving%20drugs%20to%20100%20nations%20around%20the%20world%20under%20'Vaccine%20Maitri'%20even%20as%20it%20was%20dealing%20with%20a%20public%20health%20emergency%20in%20its%20own%20backyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20India's%20global%20outreach%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20there's%20no%20question%20we%20have%20left%20a%20deeper%20imprint%20in%20the%20world%20consciousness.%20When%20they%20think%20of%20India%20today%2C%20if%20one%20is%20talking%20in%20terms%20of%20challenges%2C%20they%20see%20how%20we%20handled%20Covid%2C%20how%20we%20became%20through%20Vaccine%20Maitri%20a%20provider%20of%20vaccines%20to%20100%20countries%20across%20the%20world.%20They%20note%20how%20we%20take%20care%20of%20our%20citizens%20abroad.%20It%20could%20be%20'Operation%20Ganga'%20or%20'Kaveri'%20or%20'Ajay'.%20It%20could%20be%20the%20'Vande%20Bharat'%20mission%20during%20Covid.%20They%20see%20today%20the%20achievements%20of%20our%20businesses%20in%20projects%20abroad%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20exports%20which%20have%20gone%20up.%20They%20note%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20enormous%20progress%20that%20India%20itself%20is%20making.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20event%2C%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20touched%20on%20the%20burgeoning%20Indian%20economy%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20(the%20world)%20see%20today%20that%20despite%20the%20tremendous%20global%20headwinds%2C%20this%20is%20an%20economy%20that%20is%20growing%20at%208%20per%20cent.%20The%20fifth-largest%20economy%20was%2011th%20(even)%20a%20decade%20ago.%20It%20will%20be%20(the)%20third%20hopefully%20very%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20the%20world%2C%20even%20after%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20continues%20to%20face%20different%20challenges%20like%20the%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20conflict%20in%20Gaza%20and%20maritime%20concerns%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20other%20issues%2C%20some%20on%20our%20borders%2C%20some%20beyond.%20So%20the%20world%20is%20not%20without%20its%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20the%20world%20was%20%26quot%3Bfull%20of%20opportunities%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20used%20to%20thinking%20of%20a%20global%20marketplace.%20There%20is%20a%20global%20workplace%20which%20is%20happening.%20There%20is%20a%20global%20tech%20place%20which%20is%20taking%20place.%20There%20are%20new%20opportunities%20to%20board%20the%20manufacturing%20bus%2C%20which%20we%20may%20have%20missed%20in%20the%20earlier%20years.%20But%20to%20do%20all%20that%2C%20we%20need%20leadership%2C%20we%20need%20vision%2C%20we%20need%20a%20collective%20commitment%20of%20a%20nation.%20And%20if%20we%20get%20all%20those%20right%2C%20I'm%20very%20sure%20that%20those%20who%20come%20after%20me%20will%20be%20able%20to%20represent%20the%20nation%20abroad%20with%20even%20more%20effectiveness%20and%20an%20even%20greater%20sense%20of%20pride%20than%20I've%20had.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20on%20March%207%2C%20the%20EAM%20said%20India%20was%20working%20on%20major%20corridors%20both%20to%20its%20east%20and%20west%2C%20and%20once%20completed%2C%20these%20corridors%20will%20connect%20the%20Atlantic%20to%20the%20Pacific%20through%20Asia.%20Speaking%20at%20the%20Raisina%20Roundtable%20organised%20by%20the%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%20(ORF)%20in%20Tokyo%20on%20March%207%2C%20Jaishankar%20opened%20up%20on%20the%20major%20corridors%20on%20which%20India%20is%20currently%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20today%20working%20on%20major%20corridors%20both%20to%20its%20east%20and%20west.%20They%20include%20the%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Economic%20Corridor%20(IMEC)%20initiative%20through%20the%20Arabian%20peninsula%20and%20the%20international%20north-south%20transport%20corridor%20and%20towards%20east%20the%20trilateral%20highway%20in%20southeast%20Asia%20and%20the%20Chennai%20Vladivostok%20route%2C%20which%20also%20has%20polar%20implications...these%20corridors%20when%20completed%20will%20connect%20the%20Atlantic%20to%20the%20Pacific%20through%20Asia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710540540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F1gf6osf_s-jaishankar_625x300_12_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthis-is-a-different-india-today-now-able-to-seek-its-own-solutions-s-jaishankar-5247214%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Weighing%20in%20on%20the%20changing%20global%20perceptions%20of%20India%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Min