ow%2C%20which%20was%20canceled%20by%20Fox%20News%20in%202023.%20(Carlson%20has%20since%20switched%20to%20vlogging%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20and%20launching%20his%20own%20subscription%20product.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20ideas%20came%20to%20fruition%2C%20though.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20and%20his%20family%20have%20long%20argued%20that%20FTX%20customers%20would%20have%20speedily%20recovered%20their%20money%20if%20only%20bankruptcy%20lawyers%20had%20cooperated%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFocus%20almost%20exclusively%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20could%20give%20value%20back%20to%20customers%20and%20the%20Chapter%2011%20team%20is%20destroying%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Bankman-Fried%20wrote%20on%20one%20list%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFocus%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Chapter%2011%20team%20has%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20run%20FTX%2C%20it's%20colonial%2C%20run%20by%20a%20cartel%20of%20lawyers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCome%20out%20as%20extremely%20pro%20crypto%2C%20pro%20freedom%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.nysd.590940%2Fgov.uscourts.nysd.590940.410.4_1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanother%20list%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20tried%20to%20think%20of%20people%20who%20he%20could%20court%20for%20support.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20listed%20%26quot%3BAlt%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BSome%20other%20displaced%20group%3F%26quot%3B%20under%20the%20category%20of%20%26quot%3BRandom%20subgroup%20support.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bankruptcy%20court%20hearing%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20FTX%20lawyers%20said%20customers%20could%20be%20made%20whole%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20Bankman-Fried's%20lawyers%20have%20cited%20to%20argue%20for%20a%20light%20sentence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20prosecutors%20say%20that%20claim%20doesn't%20tell%20the%20full%20story.%20It%20doesn't%20account%20for%20the%20work%20that%20FTX%20lawyers%20put%20into%20liquidating%20and%20clawing%20back%20various%20investments%20Bankman-Fried%20made%20with%20customer%20money%2C%20they%20wrote.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOwners%20of%20Bitcoin%20on%20FTX's%20platform%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20cryptocurrency's%20prices%20because%20Bankman-Fried%20had%20already%20spent%20it%2C%20they%20wrote.%20Instead%2C%20they'd%20get%20the%20November%202022%20dollar%20amount%20for%20those%20currencies%20%E2%80%94%20far%20less%20than%20what%20they%20would%20be%20worth%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Former%20FTX%20chief%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20leaves%20the%20Federal%20Courthouse%20following%20a%20bail%20hearing%20ahead%20of%20his%20October%20trial%2C%20in%20New%20York%20City%20on%20July%2026%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64db5cd01f51cc001969af2e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESam%20Bankman-Fried%20knew%20some%20of%20his%20ideas%20were%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20bad.%26quot%3B%20%3Cp%3EANGELA%20WEISS%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%2C%20in%20his%20list%2C%20seemed%20cognizant%20of%20his%20political%20reputation.%20He%20donated%20primarily%20to%20Democrats%20in%20Congressional%20races.%20But%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaroline-ellison-sbf-thought-political-donations-got-high-returns-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrial%20testimony%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsbf-political-donations-2-executives-republicans-democrats-woke-prosecutors-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emessages%20obtained%20by%20prosecutors%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20participated%20in%20a%20straw%20donor%20scheme%20where%20he'd%20funnel%20FTX%20customer%20fu