ts%20that%20prevent%20fading%20and%20maintain%20your%20color%20for%20as%20long%20as%20possible%E2%80%94both%20for%20your%20hair%20health%20and%20your%20wallet.%20As%20a%20brand%20used%20in%20salons%20and%20loved%20by%20haircare%20professionals%20everywhere%2C%20you%20can%20trust%20K%C3%A9rastase%20to%20care%20for%20your%20color-treated%20hair%20at%20home.%20The%20formula%20hydrates%2C%20boosts%20shine%2C%20and%20cleanses%20gently%20without%20stripping%20hair%20of%20color.%20For%20those%20with%20thick%20color-treated%20hair%2C%20the%20Bain%20Riche%20Chroma%20Respect%20Shampoo%20offers%20a%20richer%20formula.%20For%20those%20with%20thick%20color-treated%20hair%2C%20try%20the%20Bain%20Riche%20Chroma%20Respect%20Shampoo%20which%20offers%20a%20richer%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20damaged%20hair%3Cp%3EOlaplex%20hit%20fast%20fame%20in%20the%20beauty%20community%20with%20its%20three-step%20Hair%20Repair%20System%20that%20claims%20to%20use%20a%20patented%20active%20ingredient%20to%20repair%20broken%20strands%20right%20at%20the%20molecular%20level.%20Its%20shampoo%20%E2%80%94%20free%20of%20parabens%2C%20sulfates%2C%20and%20phthalates%20%E2%80%94%20works%20to%20repair%20and%20protect%20hair%20from%20everyday%20stresses.%20It's%20also%20color-safe%2C%20like%20many%20sulfate-free%20shampoos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20you're%20here%20for%20post-keratin%20treatment%20options%2C%20it%20may%20not%20be%20worth%20the%20high%20price%3A%20Olaplex%20notes%20that%20since%20said%20treatments%20seal%20or%20laminate%20the%20hair%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20wait%20two%20to%20three%20weeks%20before%20Olaplex%20can%20be%20effective.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20fine%20hair%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20have%20fine%20hair%2C%20it's%20a%20fine%20line%20between%20shiny%20and%20greasy%2C%20clean%20and%20dry%2C%20moisturized%20and%20weighed%20down.%20With%20less%20diameter%20per%20strand%20to%20work%20with%2C%20fine%20hair%20(even%20when%20you%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20it)%20is%20quite%20delicate%20and%20easily%20affected%20by%20the%20products%20you%20choose.%20That's%20why%20it's%20important%20to%20use%20a%20shampoo%20specifically%20formulated%20for%20your%20fine%20hair.%20The%20OUAI%20Fine%20Hair%20Shampoo%20cleanses%2C%20nourishes%2C%20strengthens%2C%20and%20adds%20volume%20to%20your%20crown%20without%20weighing%20it%20down.%20Plus%2C%20it%20smells%20lovely%20and%20clean%20and%20looks%20quite%20chic%20stationed%20in%20your%20shower.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20thick%20hair%3Cp%3ELiving%20Proof%20is%20another%20cult-favorite%20brand%20with%20a%20gentle%2C%20patented%20process%20for%20reviving%20damaged%20hair.%20The%20company's%20proprietary%20%26quot%3BHealthy%20Hair%20Molecule%26quot%3B%20works%20to%20smooth%2C%20polish%2C%20and%20protect%20strands%20for%20stronger%2C%20healthier%20hair%20without%20sacrificing%20volume.%20Living%20Proof%20says%20its%20formula%20also%20repels%20dirt%20and%20excess%20oil%2C%20meaning%20hair%20stays%20clean%20for%20longer.%20That%20adds%20up%20to%20fewer%20washes%20and%20a%20longer-lasting%20color%20for%20you%2C%20making%20it%20a%20great%20pick%20for%20those%20with%20thick%20hair%20looking%20to%20prolong%20the%20time%20between%20washes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20nourishing%3Cp%3ETreat%20yourself%20to%20a%20hydrating%20cocktail%20of%20creamy%20coconut%20milk%2C%20coconut%20oil%2C%20and%20whipped%20egg-white%20proteins%20to%20bring%20back%20strength%2C%20shine%2C%20and%20moisture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20dandruff%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20struggle%20with%20dandruff%2C%20the%20Jupiter%20Balancing%20Shampoo%20is%20our%20favorite%20sulfate-free%20option%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-dandruff-shampoos%23best-sulfate-free-7%5C%22%3Ebest%20dandruff%20shampoos%3C%2Fa%3E.%20What%20makes%20this%20shampoo%20such%20a%20standout%20is%20the%20inclusion%20of%20Zinc%20pyrithione%201%25%2C%20a%20scientifically%20proven%2C%20medicated%20active%20ingredient%20used%20to%20fight%20flakes.%20Most%20dandruff%20shampoos%20are%20really%20just%20focused%20on%20scalp%20health%2C%20but%20Jupiter%20is%20formulated%20with%20plenty%20of%20ingredients%20to%20moisturize%20locks%20and%20improve%20shine.%20We%20love%20that%20it%20works%20for%20all%20hair%20types%2C%20too%2C%20including%20color-%20and%20chemically%20treated.%20Some%20use%20this%20product%20daily%2C%20while%20others%20only%20use%20it%20a%20few%20times%20a%20week%20%E2%80%93%20depends%20on%20the%20severity%20of%20your%20dandruff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20smoothing%3Cp%3EBumble%20and%20Bumble%20products%20like%20this%20one%20aim%20for%20the%20fine%20line%20between%20deep%20hydration%20and%20lightweight%2C%20barely-there%20oils.%20This%20sulfate-free%20shampoo%2C%20like%20many%20on%20this%20list%2C%20was%20whipped%20up%20specifically%20for%20coarse%20and%20brittle%20hair%20to%20make%20it%20smoother%20and%20silkier%20post-use.%20Six%20oils%20%E2%80%94%20including%20sweet%20almond%20and%20grape%20%E2%80%94%20soften%20and%20add%20shine.%20It's%20also%20cruelty-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20volume%3Cp%3EThey%20say%20everything's%20bigger%20in%20Texas%2C%20which%20explains%20how%20R%2BCo's%20Dallas%20Thickening%20Shampoo%20got%20its%20name.%20Hero%20ingredients%20like%20biotin%2C%20saw%20palmetto%20berry%20extract%2C%20and%20coconut%20oil%20work%20together%20to%20strengthen%20your%20strands%2C%20add%20fullness%2C%20boost%20shine%2C%20and%20improve%20overall%20hair%20health.%20With%20every%20lather%2C%20this%20shampoo%20nourishes%20and%20strengthens%20your%20locks%2C%20leaving%20you%20with%20the%20big%2C%20bouncy%20mane%20of%20your%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20frizz%3Cp%3EVerb%20Ghost%20Shampoo%20is%20infused%20with%20moringa%20seed%20oil%2C%20which%2C%20if%20you%20haven't%20heard%20of%20it%2C%20is%20a%20new%20MVP%20in%20the%20natural%20beauty%20community.%20It%20hails%20from%20the%20highly%20versatile%20Moringa%20oleifera%20tree%20which%20is%20known%20for%20everything%20short%20of%20performing%20miracles%3B%20it's%20drought-resistant%2C%20its%20seeds%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedaily.com%2Freleases%2F2010%2F03%2F100303082804.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20purify%20water%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20its%20leaves%20are%20believed%20to%20contain%20more%20calcium%20than%20milk.%20The%20tree's%20seed%20oil%20is%20full%20of%20hydrating%20monosaturated%20fatty%20acids%2C%20and%20Ghost%20Shampoo%20is%20meant%20to%20naturally%20smooth%20frizz%20and%20promote%20shine.%20Sunflower%20seed%20extract%20is%20included%20for%20natural%20UV%20protection%20and%20less%20color%20fading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20hydrating%3Cp%3EA%20longstanding%20sulfate-free%20favorite%2C%20SheaMoisture's%20Raw%20Shea%20Shampoo%20uses%20organic%20shea%20butter%2C%20argan%20oil%2C%20and%20vitamin%20E%20to%20smooth%20and%20balance%20hair%20that's%20dry%20or%20damaged.%20The%20company%20traces%20itself%20back%20to%201912%20in%20Sierra%20Leone%2C%20and%20it's%20been%20a%20historical%20leader%20in%20Black-owned%20haircare.%20Today%2C%20it's%20committed%20to%20ethically%20traded%20ingredients%20and%20sustainably%20produced%20products.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20clarifying%3Cp%3EHaircare%20products%20and%20environmental%20factors%20can%20take%20quite%20a%20beating%20on%20your%20mane%20over%20time.%20Gels%2C%20dry%20shampoos%2C%20and%20hairsprays%20make%20for%20show-stopping%20styles%2C%20but%20they%20can%20also%20clog%20hair%20follicles%20and%20trigger%20more%20oil%20production.%20Hard%20water%20and%20chlorine%20can%20leave%20your%20strands%20and%20scalp%20feeling%20dry%20and%20flaky.%20The%20good%20news%20is%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20avoid%20these%20things%20altogether%3B%20you%20just%20need%20a%20great%20clarifying%20shampoo%20in%20your%20rotation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20your%20hair%20is%20feeling%20dry%20as%20straw%20or%20you've%20become%20a%20little%20%3Cem%3Etoo%3C%2Fem%3E%20reliant%20on%20dry%20shampoo%2C%20The%20Ouai%20Detox%20Shampoo%20will%20bring%20your%20locks%20back%20to%20life.%20Apple%20cider%20vinegar%20helps%20exfoliate%20the%20scalp%2C%20chelating%20agents%20bind%20to%20the%20minerals%20and%20metals%20in%20hard%20water%20and%20styling%20products%20to%20remove%20buildup%2C%20and%20hydrolyzed%20keratin%20repairs%20damage%20and%20smooths%20the%20cuticle.%20All%20that%2C%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20it%20smells%20amazing%3F%20Sold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20natural%3Cp%3Eadwoa's%20vegan%20shampoo%20cleanses%20with%20mild%20cleansing%20agents%20to%20minimize%20dryness%20and%20scalp%20irritation%20and%20moisturizes%20with%20ingredients%20such%20as%20aloe%20leaf%20juice%20and%20essential%20oils.%20There%20are%20no%20sulfates%2C%20parabens%2C%20phthalates%2C%20or%20silicones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20remember%20to%20shake%20the%20bottle%20well%20before%20you%20use%20this%20shampoo%3B%20its%20oils%20may%20separate%20naturally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMost%20gentle%3Cp%3ENative's%20whole%20ethos%20is%20centered%20on%20simplicity%2C%20so%20its%20no%20wonder%20this%20shampoo%20is%20pared%20down%20to%20the%20basics%E2%80%93simple%2C%20clean%20ingredients%20that%20work.%20Plant%20oil-derived%20cleansers%20work%20to%20gently%20cleanse%20your%20strands%20while%20adding%20moisture%20for%20a%20soft%2C%20healthy%20shine.%20The%20formula%20is%20paraben-%2C%20dye-%20and%20sulfate-free%2C%20vegan%2C%20and%20cruelty-free.%20We%20love%20the%20minimalist%20packaging%20and%20fun%20scent%20combinations%20like%20Ocean%20%26amp%3B%20Timber%2C%20Warm%20Cider%20%26amp%3B%20Cinnamon%2C%20and%20Sweet%20Peach%20%26amp%3B%20Nectar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%3Cp%3EIngredients%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20finding%20a%20great%20sulfate-free%20shampoo%2C%20you%20should%20focus%20on%20what%20%3Cem%3Eisn't%20