k%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68573646.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68573646.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ED%20Arrests%20Opposition%20Leader%20Kavitha%20Amid%20Questions%20Over%20Agency%20Action%20and%20Electoral%20Bonds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F15220616%2FUntitled-design-46.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20has%20arrested%20BRS%20leader%20K%20Kavitha%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20former%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%2C%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA).%20The%20arrest%20was%20made%20in%20connection%20to%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20scam%2C%20in%20which%20Kavitha%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20being%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CSouth%20Liquor%20Lobby%E2%80%9D%20that%20played%20a%20role%20in%20influencing%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20liquor%20policy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20origin%20of%20the%20issue%20is%20with%20the%20excise%20policy%20framed%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20of%20Delhi%20for%20liquor%20trade%20in%202021%2C%20which%20was%20later%20withdrawn%20by%20Lieutenant-Governor%20Vinay%20Kumar%20Saxena%20ordering%20a%20probe.%20The%20investigations%20led%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Delhi%20and%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20relation%20to%20this%20case%2C%20ED%20has%20also%20issued%20summons%20to%20Kavitha%2C%20as%20a%20part%20of%20its%20probe%20into%20liquor%20policy.%20In%20March%202023%2C%20ED%20summoned%20her%20to%20appear%20in%20person%20in%20Delhi%20for%20questioning%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Delhi%20excise%20policy%20case.%20Kavitha%20argued%20that%20she%20had%20not%20been%20named%20in%20the%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20and%20that%20the%20summons%20were%20challenged%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20role%20of%20Kavitha%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20scam%20is%20not%20directly%20linked%20with%20her%20being%20termed%20as%20a%20proxy%20in%20South%20Group.%20South%20Group%20was%20accused%20in%20the%20liquor%20scam%20for%20gaining%20access%20to%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20liquor%20licences%20while%20paying%20a%20bribe%20to%20AAP%2C%20which%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20claims%20was%20used%20by%20AAP%20in%20elections%20of%20Goa.%20Members%20of%20the%20South%20Group%20have%20turned%20approvers%20in%20the%20case%20with%20the%20ED%20potentially%20using%20their%20statements%20for%20the%20arrest%20of%20Kavitha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20sudden%20arrest%20of%20Kavitha%20just%20before%20the%20release%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20schedule%20shows%20the%20weaponisation%20of%20central%20agencies%20against%20the%20opposition.%20These%20raids%20by%20the%20ED%20also%20come%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20emerging%20role%20of%20the%20enforcement%20directorate%E2%80%99s%20raids%20leading%20to%20the%20purchase%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20by%20business%20groups%2C%20with%20money%20being%20donated%20to%20evade%20persecution.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20role%20of%20electoral%20funding%20of%20political%20parties%20is%20where%20the%20tussle%20between%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20politicians%20is%20creating%20fault%20lines.%20Any%20mechanism%20of%20political%20funding%20other%20than%20legal%20channels%20is%20being%20used%20by%20these%20agencies%20for%20a%20crackdown%20on%20political%20party%20leaders.%20The%20BJP%20using%20central%20agencies%20has%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20squeeze%20the%20opposition%20to%20all%20forms%20of%20political%20funding.%20This%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20seen%20with%20the%20Congress%20being%20blocked%20from%20accessing%20its%20own%20bank%20accounts%20by%20the%20Income%20Tax%20agencies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20weaponisation%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20is%20an%20issue%20the%20political%20parties%20in%20India%20have%20been%20constantly%20complaining%20about.%20The%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20has%20been%20used%20against%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20opposition%20parties%20to%20arrest%20and%20detain%20people%20with%20malafide%20intentions.%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%E2%80%99s%20powers%20have%20been%20constantly%20challenged%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20by%20various%20people%20subject%20to%20its%20harrasment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOpposition%20leaders%20across%20India%20including%20leaders%20like%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20DK%C2%A0%20Shiva%20Kumar%2C%20and%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20have%20been%20subject%20to%20one%20form%20or%20another%20abuse%20of%20powers%20by%20ED.%20The%20functioning%20of%20the%20ED%20has%20also%20raised%20multiple%20challenges%20to%20officials%20of%20the%20state%20government%20who%20are%20being%20summoned%20by%20ED%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20largely%20allowing%20these%20actions%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20role%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20its%20actions%20against%20opposition%20and%20civil%20society%20were%20documented%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fahead-of-fatf-meeting-report-says-india-weaponising-terror-financing-money-laundering-laws-against-ngos%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshadow%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20later%20last%20year%2C%20which%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20Financial%20Action%20Task%20Force%20part%20of%20its%20Mutual%20Evaluation%20Review%20(MER).%20This%20report%20documents%20how%20NGOs%20were%20indiscriminately%20targeted%20under%20the%20money%20laundering%20laws%20and%20procedures.%20The%20MER%20report%20if%20and%20when%20it%20comes%20out%20could%20potentially%20disclose%20the%20scale%20of%20this%20problem%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20surveillance%20infrastructures%20and%20laws%20that%20were%20amended%20post%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20Attacks%20including%20PMLA%20in%202012%20gave%20wide%20powers%20to%20investigative%20agencies%20in%20India.%20These%20powers%20meant%20to%20stop%20terror%20financing%20give%20Law%20Enforcement%20Agencies%20(LEAs)%20like%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20unlimited%20powers%20with%20no%20oversight.%C2%A0%20We%20are%20now%20witnessing%20a%20political%20fallout%20of%20lack%20of%20accountability%20of%20these%20powers%20of%20investigative%20agencies%20being%20used%20against%20democratic%20opposition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%209%2F11%20the%20United%20States%20figured%20out%20a%20way%20to%20weaponise%20the%20dollar%20with%20its%20dominant%20position%20in%20global%20currency%20trades.%20The%20US%20threatened%20any%20and%20every%20other%20bank%2C%20country%20and%20their%20entire%20networks%20that%20were%20helping%20finance%20terrorists%20to%20be%20cut%20off%20from%20the%20currency%20trades.%20US%20officials%20later%20used%20these%20mechanisms%20against%20Iran%2C%20China%20and%20Russia%20as%20part%20of%20their%20geo-political%20strategies.%20Similar%20to%20the%20US%2C%20India%20is%20weaponizing%20its%20domestic%20currency%20and%20its%20transfer%20against%20political%20opposition%20instead%20of%20real%20terrorists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710521981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F15220616%2FUntitled-design-46.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fed-arrests-opposition-leader-kavitha-amid-questions-over-agency-action-and-electoral-bonds%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Surveillance%20infrastructures%20and%20laws%20amended%20post%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20Attacks%20including%20PMLA%20in%202012%20gave%20wid