%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20high%20courts%2C%20civil%20servants%2C%20academics%2C%20journalists%20and%20members%20of%20civil%20society%20%E2%80%93%20will%20visit%20Manipur%20to%20hold%20tribunal%20hearings%20across%20the%20state%20to%20directly%20hear%20testimonies%20of%20the%20local%20people%20on%20violence%20in%20the%20state.%20These%20in-person%20visits%20and%20sittings%20will%20be%20held%20between%20mid-March%20and%20mid-May%2C%202024.%20While%20the%20interim%20report%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20out%20in%20mid-June%2C%20the%20full%20report%20will%20be%20made%20available%20to%20the%20public%20in%20mid-August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20PUCL%2C%20there%20are%20five%20objectives%20before%20the%20tribunal%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ea.%20Document%20the%20violations%20suffered%20by%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur%20with%20specific%20attention%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20life%2C%20sexual%20violence%20and%20violence%20suffered%20by%20children%2C%20women%20including%20pregnant%20women%20and%20the%20elderly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Eb.%20Examine%20and%20analyse%20the%20performance%20and%20responsibilities%20of%20the%20constitutional%20authorities%20by%20documenting%20the%20action%20taken%20to%20prevent%20the%20violence%2C%20provide%20access%20to%20remedy%20and%20justice%2C%20investigate%20and%20prosecute%20crimes%2C%20and%20in%20all%20other%20ways%20to%20provide%20redressal%20of%20violations%20and%20make%20efforts%20to%20establish%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ec.%20Examine%20the%20role%20of%20all%20security%20agencies%20as%20well%20as%20government%20functionaries%20at%20all%20levels%20of%20the%20state%20and%20central%20governments%20in%20ensuring%20law%20and%20order%20and%20also%20examine%20the%20role%20of%20independent%20national%20and%20state-based%20institutions%20in%20protecting%20human%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ed.%20Examine%20existing%20documentation%20on%20the%20Manipur%20situation%20and%20analyse%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20continuing%20violence%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ee.%20Propose%20recommendations%20to%20repair%20the%20torn%20social%2C%20cultural%20and%20political%20fabric%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ethnic%20strife%2C%20which%20began%20on%20May%203%20last%20year%2C%20continues%20to%20rock%20the%20state%20even%20after%20nine%20months.%20Over%20200%20people%20have%20been%20reportedly%20killed%2C%20and%20many%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20continue%20to%20live%20in%20refugee%20camps%20fearing%20violence.%20Both%20Kukis%20and%20Meities%20have%20expressed%20deep%20mistrust%20with%20the%20state%20and%20Union%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710518358000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F17200237%2FScreenshot-2023-05-17-at-8.02.32-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpucl-announces-independent-citizens-tribunal-to-probe-manipur-violence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20panel%20%E2%80%93%20which%20will%20comprise%20eminent%20retired%20judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20high%20courts%2C%20civil%20servants%2C%20academics%2C%20journalists%20and%20members%20of%20civil%20society%20%E2%80%93%20will%20visit%20Manipur%20to%20hold%20tribunal%20hearings%20across%20the%20state.%20The%20interim%20report%20will%20be%20out%20in%20mid-June.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpucl-announces-independent-citizens-tribunal-to-probe-manipur-violence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Staqu%20unveils%20AI%20tool%20in%20collaboration%20with%20UP%20police%20to%20nab%20criminals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710517742000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F15%2Ffull%2F1710517593-6463.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fstart-ups%2F