20some%20of%20the%20environmental%20controversies%20that%20Vedanta%20has%20been%20embroiled%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBlack%20gold%3F%20Locals%20don%E2%80%99t%20agree%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20data%20provided%20by%20the%20SBI%20(from%202019%20to%202024)%2C%20Vedanta%20Limited%20alone%20donated%20Rs%20375.65%20crore%20in%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20unknown%20political%20parties.%20Vedanta%20Limited%20bought%20its%20first%20set%20of%20bonds%20worth%20Rs.%2039.65%20crore%20on%20April%2016%2C%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20April%2025%2C%202019%2C%20PTI%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fenergy%2Foil-gas%2Fvedanta-gets-green-nod-for-rs-12000-cr-oil-gas-expansion-project-in-rajasthan%2Farticleshow%2F69041430.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20Vedanta%20received%20environmental%20clearance%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%20(MoEFCC)%20for%20the%20expansion%20of%20its%20oil%20and%20gas%20operations%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20a%20project%20it%20planned%20to%20invest%20Rs.%2012%2C000%20crores%20into.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVedanta%2C%20under%20its%20vertical%20Cairn%20Oil%20and%20Gas%2C%20had%20proposed%20to%20expand%20its%20existing%20onshore%20oil%20and%20gas%20production%20%E2%80%93%20from%203%2C00%2C000%20barrels%20oil%20per%20day%20or%20BOPD%2C%20to%204%2C00%2C000%20BOPD%2C%20and%20from%20165%20million%20standard%20cubic%20feet%20per%20day%20or%20MMSCFD%20to%20750%20MMSCFD%20%E2%80%93%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9CRJ-ON-90%2F1%E2%80%9D%20block%20located%20in%20Barmer%20district%20in%20Rajasthan.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20Vedanta%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cairnindia.com%2FPages%2FRajasthan.aspx%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20block%20RJ-ON-90%2F1%20is%20spread%20over%203%2C111%20square%20kilometers%20in%20Barmer%20district.%20The%20block%20has%20%E2%80%9Ccontributed%20USD%2023.7%20billion%20to%20the%20nation%20and%20the%20state%20exchequer%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20on%20March%2031%2C%202023%2C%20and%20cumulative%20production%20from%20the%20Rajasthan%20block%20has%20crossed%20700%20MMBBLS%20or%20one%20million%20barrels%20of%20oil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C13%20dry%20wells%20were%20drilled%20in%20Rajasthan%20block%20before%20Cairn%20struck%20%E2%80%98black%20gold%E2%80%99%20in%20the%2014th%20well.%20The%20organisation%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20since%2C%20with%20numerous%20discoveries%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20block%2C%20bringing%20a%20number%20of%20fields%20to%20production%2C%20and%20gearing%20towards%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20website%20reads.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20black%20gold%20has%20been%20turning%20water%20sources%20black%20too%2C%20making%20water%20unsuitable%20for%20human%20and%20animal%20consumption%2C%20and%20even%20agriculture%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2FBarmer-Farmers-Call-Postponing-Aug-31-Public-Hearing-Cairn-India%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20farmers%20in%20the%20locality%20as%20saying.%20Though%20district%20officials%20ordered%20Cairn%20to%20supply%20drinking%20water%20to%20some%20villages%20in%20the%20area%2C%20locals%20alleged%20that%20this%20was%20not%20done.%20Cairn%2F%20Vedanta%20refuted%20these%20allegations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20it%20bought%20its%20first%20electoral%20bonds%20in%20April%202019%2C%20Vedanta%20continued%20its%20buying%20spree%3A%20it%20bought%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%2010%20crore%20on%20May%2010%2C%202019%2C%20and%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%203%20crore%20on%20October%209%2C%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%