rore%20worth%20of%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20rat-miners%20garnered%20praise%20for%20their%20herculean%20efforts%20to%20rescue%20workers.%20However%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20group%2C%20Vakeel%20Hassan%2C%20had%20his%20home%20in%20New%20Delhi%20razed%20by%20a%20bulldozer%20for%20being%20built%20in%20an%20unauthorised%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20Seema%20Chishti)%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710508550000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01140335%2FGACaXNpbYAASMBx.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fnavayuga-engineering-responsible-for-building-the-collapsed-silkyara-tunnel-bought-rs-55-cr-of-bonds%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20company%20faced%20IT%20raids%20by%20the%20Centre%20on%20October%2026%2C%202018.%20It%20bought%20its%20first%20tranche%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%2030%20crore%2C%20six%20months%20later.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fnavayuga-engineering-responsible-for-building-the-collapsed-silkyara-tunnel-bought-rs-55-cr-of-bonds%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20a%20Democracy%2C%20Paper%20Ballot%20Is%20the%20Gold%20Standard%20for%20Elections.%20Per%20Law%2C%20Use%20of%20EVM%20Is%20an%20Option%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09194755%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-7.39.03%25E2%2580%25AFPM_cleanup-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%2C%20in%20its%20writ%20petition%20pending%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20has%20pleaded%20that%20the%20print-out%20of%20the%20voter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%20slips%20must%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20voter%20who%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20must%20be%20able%20to%20deposit%20them%20in%20the%20VVPAT%20Box.%20It%20further%20adds%20that%20these%20slips%20must%20be%20counted%20and%20cross-verified%20by%20the%20electronic%20count%20in%20the%20EVMs%2C%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20top%20court%20in%20%3Cem%3ESubramanian%20Swamy%20v.%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2013).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20plea%20is%20also%20in%20accordance%20with%20Rule%2056(D)(4)(b)%20of%20Conduct%20of%20Election%20Rules%2C%201961%2C%20which%20provides%20that%20the%20count%20of%20VVPATs%20shall%20prevail%20over%20the%20count%20reflected%20in%20EVMs%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20discrepancy%20between%20the%20votes%20displayed%20on%20the%20control%20unit%20and%20the%20counting%20of%20the%20paper%20slips%2C%20amend%20the%20result%20sheet%20in%20Form%2020%20as%20per%20the%20paper%20slips%20count.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20rule%20is%20a%20statutory%20admission%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20finally%20the%20VVPAT%20slips%20which%20accurately%20captures%20the%20will%20of%20the%20voter%20and%20that%20errors%20in%20the%20results%20captured%20in%20the%20EVMs%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out%20for%20any%20given%20reason.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20counter-affidavit%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20said%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C100%25%20verification%20of%20VVPAT%20is%20a%20regressive%20step%20and%20takes%20the%20country%20back%20to%20manual%20counting%20of%20ballots.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Commission%2C%20the%20purpose%20of%20VVPATs%20is%20only%20to%20ensure%20that%20voters%20can%20verify%20that%20their%20vote%20has%20been%20cast%20as%20intended.%20This%20means%20that%20VVPATs%20were%20mere%20%E2%80%98bioscopes%E2%80%99%20and%20not%20a%20device%20to%20verify%20and%20audit%20the%20casting%2C%20recording%20and%20counting%20of%20votes%20as%20intended%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ECI%20also%20stated%20that%20any%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20VVPATs%20to%20be%20cross-verified%20will%20pose%20an%20administrative%20challenge%2C%20implying%20that%20the%20comfort%20of%20election%20officials%20was%20more%20important%20than%20electoral%20democracy.%20It%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ealso%20lied%20that%20the%20ballot%20counting%20system%20used%20to%20take%20up%20to%20six%20days%20and%20it%20will%20take%20more%20time%20if%20VVPATs%20are%20counted%20and%20recounted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Commission%20also%20said%20that%20Indian%20voters%20do%20not%20have%20a%20%E2%80%98fundamental%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20get%20their%20vote%20verified%20through%20VVPATs.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ECI%20has%20been%20deliberately%20promoting%20the%20notion%20that%20paper%20slips%20and%20ballot%20papers%20are%20primitive%20and%20counting%20them%20will%20take%20India%20back%20to%20the%20stone%20age.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20a%20democracy%2C%20paper%20ballot%20is%20the%20gold%20standard%20for%20elections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20their%20autocratic%20arrogance%2C%20the%20Commission%20refuses%20to%20realise%20that%20in%20any%20genuine%20democracy%2C%20paper%20ballot%20is%20the%20gold%20standard%20for%20elections.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.electiondefense.org%2Fpaper-ballots%5C%22%3ENational%20Election%20Defense%20Coalition%20of%20USA%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20using%20paper%20may%20sound%20antiquated%2C%20the%20consensus%20among%20election%20security%20experts%20is%20that%20nothing%20else%20provides%20the%20needed%20reliability%2C%20security%2C%20and%20transparency.%20Durable%2C%20voter%20marked%20paper%20ballots%20are%20appropriate%20technology%20for%20public%20elections.%20Hand%20Counted%20Paper%20Ballots%20are%20considered%20the%20%E2%80%9CGold%20Standard%E2%80%9D%20of%20democratic%20elections.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.electiondefense.org%2Fpaper-ballots%5C%22%3EOnly%20paper%20ballots%20provide%20physical%20proof%20of%20the%20voter%E2%80%99s%20intent.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Paper%20ballots%20can%20be%20safely%20recounted%20in%20case%20of%20a%20contested%20result.%20Counting%20paper%20ballots%20in%20public%20provides%20100%25%20oversight%20and%20transparency%E2%80%A6.%20Unlike%20computer%20voting%20systems%3A%C2%A0%20-paper%20ballots%20cannot%20break%20down%20or%20malfunction%3B%20%E2%80%93%20paper%20ballots%20are%20not%20programmed%20secretly%20by%20unaccountable%20private%20corporations%3B%20%E2%80%93%20paper%20ballots%20cannot%20be%20hacked%20or%20rigged.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-case-for-bringing-paper-ballots-back%5C%22%3EThe%20Case%20for%20Bringing%20Paper%20Ballots%20Back%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%20myth%20that%20using%20EVMs%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20conduct%20elections%2C%20the%20Representation%20of%20People%E2%80%99s%20Act%2C%201951%20(RPA)%20and%20Conduct%20of%20Election%20Rules%2C%201961%2C%20clearly%20provide%20for%20voting%20and%20counting%20through%20ballot%20paper.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%5BThe%5D%20m%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eanner%20of%20voting%20at%20elections.%20At%20every%20election%20where%20a%20poll%20is%20taken%2C%20votes%20shall%20be%20given%20by%20ballot%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20as%20may%20be%20prescribed%20and%2C%20save%20as%20expressly%20provided%20by%20this%20Act%2C%20no%20votes%20shall%20be%20received%20by%20proxy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Section%2059%20of%20the%20RP%20Act%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flddashboard.legislative.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FA1951-43.pdf%5C%22%3Esays%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESection%2061A%20provides%20for%20voting%20machines%20at%20elections.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNotwithstanding%20anything%20contained%20in%20this%20Act%20or%20the%20rules%20made%20thereunder%2C%20the%20giving%20and%20recording%20of%20votes%20by%20voting%20machines%20in%20such%20manner%20as%20may%20be%20prescribed%2C%20may%20be%20adopted%20in%20such%20%5Ba%5D%20constituency%20or%20constituencies%20as%20the%20Election%20Commission%20may%2C%20having%20regard%20to%20the%20circumstances%20of%20each%20case%2C%20specify.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Conduct%20of%20Election%20Rules%2C%201961%20(CER)%20has%20a%20full%20part%20and%20chapter%20(Part%20IV%20and%20Chapter%20I)%20on%20%E2%80%9CVoting%20by%20Ballots%E2%80%9D.%20Rule%2038%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.parlament.cat%2Fdocument%2Fintrade%2F181099%5C%22%3Especific%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIssue%20of%20ballot%20papers%20to%20electors.%20(1)%20Every%20ballot%20paper%20before%20it%20is%20issued%20to%20an%20elector%2C%20and%20the%20counterfoil%20attached%20thereto%20shall%20be%20stamped%20on%20the%20back%20with%20such%20distinguishing%20mark%20as%20the%20Election%20Commission%20may%20direct%2C%20and%20every%20ballot%20paper%2C%20before%20it%20is%20issued%2C%20shall%20be%20signed%20in%20full%20on%20its%20back%20by%20the%20presiding%20officer.%20(2)%20At%20the%20time%20of%20issuing%20a%20ballot%20paper%20to%20an%20elector%2C%20the%20polling%20officer%20shall%E2%80%94(a)%20record%20on%20its%20counterfoil%20the%20electoral%20roll%20number%20of%20the%20elector%20as%20entered%20in%20the%20marked%20copy%20of%20the%20electoral%20roll%3B%20%5B(b)%20obtain%20the%20signature%20or%20thumb%20impression%20of%20that%20elector%20on%20the%20said%20counterfoil%3B%20and%20(c)%20mark%20the%20name%20of%20the%20elector%20in%20the%20marked%20copy%20of%20the%20electoral%20roll%20to%20indicate%20that%20a%20ballot%20paper%20has%20been%20issued%20to%20him%2C%20without%20however%20recording%20therein%20the%20serial%20number%20of%20the%20ballot%20paper%20issued%20to%20that%20elector.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20separate%20Chapter%20(Chapter%20II)%20for%20%E2%80%9CVoting%20by%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machine%E2%80%9D%20laying%20down%20the%20process%20and%20procedure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20as%20per%20the%20law%2C%20the%20use%20of%20ballot%20paper%20is%20the%20norm%20and%20use%20of%20EVM%20is%20an%20option.%20There%20is%20more.%20Section%20135%20of%20RPA%20provides%20for%20consequences%20for%20unauthorised%20removal%20of%20a%20ballot%20paper%20(BP)%20from%20the%20polling%20station.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESection%20136%20of%20the%20RP%20Act%20provides%20for%20consequences%20for%3A%20(i)%20Defacing%20or%20destroying%20a%20BP%20(ii)%20Supplying%20a%20BP%20without%20authority%20to%20any%20person%20and%20(iii)%20Fraudulently%20putting%20anything%20into%20a%20Ballot%20Box%20other%20than%20a%20BP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERule%2030%20of%20the%20CER%20provides%20for%20a%20counterfoil%20to%20be%20attached%20to%20the%20ballot%20paper%20to%20ensure%20security%20of%20voting.%20Rule%2033%20of%20CER%20provides%20for%20securing%20and%20sealing%20a%20ballot%20box%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20tampering%20can%20take%20place.%20The%20said%20rule%20also%20provides%20that%20each%20ballot%20box%20shall%20have%20labels%2C%20both%20inside%20and%20outside%2C%20which%20will%20be%20shown%20to%20the%20polling%20agents%20to%20confirm%20that%20the%20box%20is%20empty%20and%20bears%20the%20required%20labels.%20Rule%2038%20of%20CER%20provides%20that%20before%20a%20ballot%20paper%20is%20issued%20to%20an%20elector%2C%20the%20counterfoil%20attached%20to%20it%20shall%20be%20stamped%20on%20the%20back%20with%20a%20distinguishing%20mark%20and%20signed%20by%20the%20presiding%20officer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20appears%20that%20law%20and%20rules%2C%20as%20they%20stand%20today%2C%20are%20primarily%20for%20ballot%20papers%20and%20ballot%20boxes%20not%20EVMs.%20Hence%2C%20the%20argument%20that%20reverting%20to%20them%20would%20be%20time-consuming%20and%20require%20an%20amendment%20to%20the%20RP%20Act%20is%20only%20a%20myth%20to%20hood-wink%20the%20gullible%20citizens%20of%20the%20country.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20seems%20that%20because%20of%20its%20%E2%80%9Ctechnology%20obsession%E2%80%9D%2C%20ECI%20has%20feverishly%20adopted%20the%20EVM%20in%20violation%20of%20Section%2061A%20of%20the%20RP%20Act%20without%20any%20justifiable%20circumstances%20or%20cogent%20reasons.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20law%20permits%20the%20ECI%20to%20use%20EVMs%20for%20elections%20only%20on%20a%20case-to-case%20basis%2C%20only%20for%20justifiable%20reasons%2C%20and%20not%20entirely%20as%20they%20claim.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20the%20ECI%20should%20return%20to%20voting%20through%20ballot%20papers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20claim%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20debunked%20is%20the%20ECI%20saying%20%3Cspan%3Ethat%20since%20the%20elections%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20announced%20soon%2C%20only%20EVMs%20can%20be%20used%20as%20they%20are%20ready.%20This%20is%20a%20complete%20falsehood%20as%20no%20EVM%20can%20be%20prepared%20for%20any%20constituency%20till%20the%20nomination%20and%20scrutiny%20of%20candidates%20is%20completed%20and%20the%20last%20date%20for%20withdrawal%20of%20candidature%20has%20passed.%20The%20final%20list%20of%20candidates%20for%20each%20constituency%20is%20prepared%20and%20loaded%20into%20the%20machine%20only%20after%20this%20has%20been%20done.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBallot%20papers%20can%20also%20only%20be%20printed%20after%20this%20stage.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20that%20is%20needed%20is%20to%20shortlist%20printing%20presses%20and%20have%20them%20cleared%20for%20security.%20The%20logistics%20of%20procuring%20ballot%20boxes%20and%20other%20material%20could%20be%20done%20easily%20as%20they%20are%20already%20in%20use%20for%20panchayat%20and%20local%20body%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20imperative%2C%20therefore%2C%20that%20India%20returns%20to%20ballot%20paper.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ECI%20and%20those%20who%20support%20the%20usage%20of%20EVMs%20claim%20that%20it%20will%20encourage%20booth%20capturing%20and%20ballot-stuffing.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20prove%20their%20point%2C%20they%20have%20gone%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20quoting%20the%20presiding%20officer%20of%20Chandigarh%20mayoral%20elections%20deliberately%20invalidating%20eight%20valid%20paper%20votes.%20What%20they%20are%20not%20revealing%20is%20that%20while%20tampering%20with%20paper%20votes%20can%20be%20caught%20red-handed%2C%20manipulation%20of%20thousands%20of%20votes%20in%20the%20EVMs%20cannot%20be%20detected.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20booth%20capturing%20and%20ballot-stuffing%20used%20to%20take%20place%20when%20the%20supervision%2C%20security%2C%20transportation%20and%20communication%20systems%20were%20primitive.%20That%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20case.%20Now%20senior%20election%20officials%2C%20ECI%20observers%2C%20police%20and%20flying%20squads%20can%20observe%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20polling%20booths%20through%20CCTV%20cameras%20and%20can%20intervene%20instantly%20in%20the%20event%20of%20any%20mischief.%20Sensitive%20booths%20are%20guarded%20by%20armed%20police%20with%20orders%20to%20shoot%20in%20case%20of%20any%20booth%20capturing%20and%20ballot%20stuffing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20the%20ECI%20should%20heed%20the%20demand%20of%20the%20people%20and%20return%20to%20voting%20through%20ballot%20papers%20as%20envisaged%20in%20the%20law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EM.G.%20Devasahayam%20is%20a%20former%20Army%20and%20IAS%20Officer.%20He%20is%20Coordinator%20of%20Citizens%20Commission%20on%20Elections%20and%20editor%20of%20the%20book%20Electoral%20Democracy%E2%80%94An%20Inquiry%20into%20the%20Fairness%20and%20Integrity%20of%20Elections%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EMehmood%20Pracha%20is%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20advocate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710507641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09194755%2FScreenshot-2023-11-09-at-7.39.03%25E2%2580%25AFPM_cleanup-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fin-a-democracy-paper-ballot-is-the-gold-standard-for-elections-per-law-use-of-evm-is-an-option%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20law%20permits%20the%20ECI%20to%20use%20EVMs%20for%20elections%20only%20on%20a%20case-to-case%20basis%2C%20only%20for%20justifiable%20reasons%2C%20and%20not%20entirely%20as%20being%20claimed.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fin-a-democracy-paper-ballot-is-the-gold-standard-for-elections-per-law-use-of-evm-is-an-option%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Decorative%20crystal%20prisms%2C%20bird%20baths%20and%20ketchup%20-%20what%20to%20expect%20from%20Meghan's%20new%20brand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710507060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-meghan-duchess-of-sussex_6491414.jpg%3F20240315171245%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fduchess-of-sussex-decorative-crystal-prisms-bird-baths-and-ketchup-what-to-expect-from-meghans-new-brand-13095262%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bird%20baths%20%26quot%3Bfor%20birds%20to%20bathe%20in%26quot%3B%2C%20pet%20collars%2C%20decorative%20crystal%20prisms%20