3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20spoke%20to%20chefs%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20India%20and%20even%20got%20an%20opportunity%20to%20relish%20some%20of%20their%20food%20at%20Gopal%20Maidan.%20Despite%20the%20difference%20in%20their%20preparation%20styles%20and%20ingredients%20used%2C%20something%20unified%20the%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Vasantha%20from%20the%20Irula%20tribe%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20said%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(finger%20millet)%20is%20the%20primary%20cereal%20in%20her%20village.%20They%20use%20it%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eballs.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Santi%20Bairak%20from%20the%20Chik%20Baraik%20tribe%20of%20Odisha%20uses%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20make%20fritters%2C%20%3Cem%3Esamosa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Emanchurian%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20even%20milkshakes.%20Then%20there%20is%20also%20Swati%20from%20the%20Oraon%20tribe%20who%20makes%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20cakes%20and%20pastries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20taste%20of%20their%20dishes%20%E2%80%94%20umami%2C%20spicy%20and%20sweet%20%E2%80%94%20are%20poles%20apart%2C%20the%20reason%20for%20using%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20the%20same%20%E2%80%94%20health%20benefits%20and%20easy%20access.%20And%20it%20got%20more%20interesting%20when%20Vasantha%20took%20a%20leaf%20out%20of%20Santi%E2%80%99s%20culinary%20book%2C%20went%20back%20home%2C%20and%20experimented%20with%20it!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Vasantha%2C%20Santi%20and%20other%20chefs%2C%20their%20role%20goes%20beyond%20cooking%20and%20showcasing%20their%20food%3B%20it%20is%20a%20way%20to%20connect%20their%20community%20with%20the%20outside%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFood%20is%20actually%20the%20easiest%20way%20to%20initiate%20a%20conversation%20with%20strangers.%20However%2C%20though%20people%20may%20connect%20via%20%3Cem%3EPunjabi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EGujarati%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20Goan%20cuisine%2C%20rarely%20are%20they%20aware%20of%20tribal%20cuisine.%20Part%20of%20the%20problem%20is%20the%20blanket%20labelling%20of%20tribal%20foods%20under%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98indigenous%E2%80%99%2C%20when%20in%20fact%20our%20food%20is%20as%20diverse%20as%20it%20can%20get.%20So%2C%20when%20people%20visit%20my%20stall%2C%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20educate%20them%20about%20our%20tribe%E2%80%99s%20history%20and%20why%20we%20use%20certain%20ingredients%20the%20way%20we%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Palash%20Mallick%20from%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Lodha%20tribe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20happy%20that%20the%20sales%20of%20his%20star%20dish%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Edudh%20puli%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(rice%20dumplings)%20have%20increased%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20fried%20dumplings%20are%20made%20with%20rice%20flour%2C%20coconut%2C%20jaggery%20and%20milk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20stalls%20away%2C%20Pritesh%20Kumar%20from%20the%20Oraon%20tribe%E2%80%99s%20Khalko%20clan%20excitedly%20narrated%20the%20fascinating%20story%20behind%20each%20dish%20while%20offering%20free%20samples.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3Ebaas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(bamboo)%20pickle%20is%20good%20for%20your%20blood%2C%20and%20the%3Cem%3E%20demta%20chutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20made%20from%20red%20weaver%20ants%20is%20rich%20in%20protein%20and%20calcium.%20%3Cem%3EJamun%3C%2Fem%3E%20powder%20helps%20control%20sugar%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20potential%20customer%20at%20his%20stall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0958_11zon-1710505545-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20these%20chefs%20from%20the%20tribal%20community%2C%20their%20role%20goes%20beyond%20cooking%20and%20showcasing%20their%20food%3B%20it%20is%20a%20way%20to%20connect%20their%20community%20with%20the%20outside%20world.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0958_11zon-1710505545-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0958_11zon-1710505545-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0958_11zon-1710505545-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0958_11zon-1710505545-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0958_11zon-1710505545-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0958_11zon-1710505545-2048x1152.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0958_11zon-1710505545-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344985%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFor%20these%20home%20chefs%2C%20their%20role%20goes%20beyond%20cooking%20and%20showcasing%20their%20food%3B%20it%20is%20a%20way%20to%20connect%20their%20community%20with%20the%20outside%20world.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20how%20cuisine%20helps%20uplift%20his%20community%2C%20Pritesh%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20get%20to%20tell%20our%20stories%20through%20cuisine%20by%20shedding%20light%20on%20ingredients%2C%20preparation%20methods%2C%20taste%20and%20more.%20Get%20us%20more%20stalls%20like%20these.%20We%20will%20not%20only%20survive%20but%20also%20flourish.%20We%20offer%20foods%20that%20may%20not%20be%20available%20everywhere%20in%20India.%20Every%20generation%20closely%20guards%20these%20recipes.%20It%20is%20our%20fourth%20time%20here%20%5Bat%20the%20conclave%5D.%20Every%20year%2C%20we%20receive%20orders%20from%20across%20India%20once%20we%20go%20back%20home.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMentioning%20the%20controversial%20plant%20of%20%3Cem%3Emahua%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3E(Madhuca%20longifolia)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EMahua%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20unfortunately%20only%20popular%20as%20an%20alcoholic%20drink%20and%20hence%20people%20assume%20our%20community%20is%20backwards%20due%20to%20this.%20What%20many%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20is%20that%20%3Cem%3Emahua%3C%2Fem%3E%20can%20be%20used%20to%20make%20pickles%20and%20cookies%20as%20well.%20They%20have%20several%20health%20benefits.%20We%20aim%20to%20bring%20these%20dishes%20into%20the%20mainstream.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritesh%20and%20his%20family%20earn%20five%20months%E2%80%99%20worth%20of%20earnings%20within%20two%20days%20at%20Samvaad.%20He%20expressed%20hope%20that%20future%20generations%20will%20be%20eager%20to%20learn%20these%20recipes%20now%20due%20to%20its%20increasing%20market%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeeta%20Sandil%20of%20the%20Munda%20tribe%2C%20who%20was%20participating%20in%20the%20conclave%20for%20the%20second%20time%2C%20said%20she%20had%20seen%20similar%20profits%20because%20of%20Samvaad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20we%20were%20the%20only%20ones%2C%20but%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20to%20see%20so%20many%20tribal%20communities.%20We%20sold%20a%20lot%20last%20year%2C%20so%20we%20are%20back%20with%20several%20new%20additions%20like%20chicken%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20duck%20meat%2C%20%3Cem%3Edhuska%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Emasoor%20dal%20pakoda%3C%2Fem%3E%20(lentil%20fritters)%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekhasi%20%3C%2Fem%3Epieces%20(goat%20legs).%20These%20dishes%20are%20good%20for%20bones%2C%20kidney%20stones%2C%20heart%20and%20gut.%20We%20prepare%20all%20the%20spices%20at%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeing%20the%20positive%20response%20here%2C%20Geeta%20expressed%20her%20desire%20to%20quit%20her%20restaurant%20job%20and%20start%20her%20own%20food%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamvaad%20is%20helping%20participants%20like%20Geeta%20who%20wish%20to%20walk%20on%20the%20entrepreneurial%20road.%20For%20instance%2C%20this%20year%2C%20it%20tied%20up%20with%20Zomato%20to%20home-deliver%20traditional%20cuisines%20prepared%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344574%2Ftata-samvaad-tribal-conclave-preserves-lost-heritage-artisans-sell-handicrafts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20the%20conclave%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20Jamshedpur%20for%20five%20days!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20not%20all%2C%20tribal%20cuisine%20has%20been%20taking%20over%20luxury%20dining%20tables%2C%20as%20TSF%20collaborated%20with%20Indian%20Hotels%20Company%20Limited%20(IHCL)%20to%20put%20up%20food%20carnivals%20and%20workshops%20at%20the%20Taj%20chain%20of%20hotels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%3A%20Gopi%20Karelia)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710506256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0960_11zon-1710505353-scaled.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344924%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tata%20Samvaad%2C%20a%20tribal%20conclave%20in%20Jamshedpur%20by%20the%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%2C%20showcased%20diverse%20indigenous%20cuisines%20from%2035%20tribes.%20Around%20140%20home%20chefs%20shared%20unique%20dishes%20like%20ragi%20samosa%2C%20demta%20chutney%2C%20dudh%20puli%2C%20etc%2C%20highlighting%20the%20cultural%20significance%20of%20their%20ingredients.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Gopi%20Karelia%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344924%2Ftata-samvaad-conclave-showcase-tribal-cuisine-dishes-by-home-chefs-entrepreneurs%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Finland%20lays%20out%20plans%20to%20block%20asylum%20seekers%20arriving%20from%20Russia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710505860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-finland-border-russia_6491157.jpg%3F20240315123753%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffinland-lays-out-plans-to-block-asylum-seekers-arriving-from-russia-13095252%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Finland%20is%20planning%20to%20adopt%20temporary%20legislation%20that%20will%20allow%20authorities%20to%20block%20asylum%20seekers%20arriving%20from%20Russia%2C%20the%20government%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A121%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffinland-lays-out-plans-to-block-asylum-seekers-arriving-from-russia-13095252%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ffinland-lays-out-plans-to-block-asylum-seekers-arriving-from-russia-13095252%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ffinland-lays-out-plans-to-block-asylum-seekers-arriving-from-russia-13095252%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Abdullah%20Ibrahim%3A%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20Master%20Pianist%20Is%20Going%20on%20a%20World%20Tour%20At%26nbsp%3B90%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F15172841%2FScreenshot-2024-03-15-at-5.28.00-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAbdullah%20Ibrahim%2C%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20most%20distinguished%20pianist%2C%20was%20born%20on%209%20October%201934%20in%20Cape%20Town.%20This%20year%20marks%20not%20only%20his%2090th%20birthday%20but%20also%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.musicinafrica.net%2Fmagazine%2Fsa-jazz-icon-abdullah-ibrahim-announces-cape-town-and-pretoria-shows%5C%22%3Estart%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabdullahibrahim.co.za%2Ftour%2F%5C%22%3Eworld%20tour%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Christine%20Lucia%20has%20studied%20Ibrahim%E2%80%99s%20work%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1080%2F09681220208567341%3Fcasa_token%3Ds_J5R4VU3gQAAAAA%3A8mFbTGwVjt33LO-Tj1nPrhzbiylBiKQgGUYyE_rnIegjjG9Z5exOJFp-6c2No3SOGlV9razGz8_VWtk%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20research%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fprofile%2FChristine-Lucia-3%2Fpublication%2F333676644_Abdullah_Ibrahim_and_%2527African_Pianism_%2527_in_South_Africa%2Flinks%2F5cfe8c51a6fdccd13091b72c%2FAbdullah-Ibrahim-and-African-Pianism-in-South-Africa.pdf%5C%22%3Earticles%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20him.%20We%20asked%20her%20why%20he%20is%20so%20important.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Abdullah%20Ibrahim%20and%20what%20shaped%20him%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabdullahibrahim.co.za%2Fbiography%2F%5C%22%3EAbdullah%20Ibrahim%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20finest%20jazz%20pianist-composer%20that%20South%20Africa%20has%20ever%20produced%20%E2%80%93%20even%20in%20such%20a%20jazz-rich%20country.%20He%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20equivalent%20of%20the%20US%20jazz%20star%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Fbiography%2FDuke-Ellington%5C%22%3EDuke%20Ellington%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20because%20his%20legacy%20lies%20not%20only%20in%20his%20live%20performances%20or%20multiple%20recordings%20but%20also%20in%20his%20large%20number%20of%20compositions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20brought%20up%20going%20by%20the%20name%20Dollar%20Brand%20and%20was%20shaped%20personally%20by%20his%20mixed-race%20parentage%20and%20by%20growing%20up%20in%20the%20mixed-race%20area%20of%20central%20Cape%20Town%20formerly%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sahistory.org.za%2Fplace%2Fdistrict-six-cape-town%5C%22%3EDistrict%20Six%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20area%20was%20demolished%20during%20the%201970s%20by%20the%20white%20minority%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sahistory.org.za%2Farticle%2Fhistory-apartheid-south-africa%5C%22%3Eapartheid%3C%2Fa%3E%20regime%20and%2060%2C000%20people%20were%20forced%20to%20live%20far%20outside%20Cape%20Town%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sahistory.org.za%2Fplace%2Fathlone-or-cape-flats-cape-town%5C%22%3ECape%20Flats%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20was%20shaped%20by%20this%20violent%20political%20landscape%20of%20racism%20and%20oppression.%20As%20a%20young%20man%20he%20was%20also%20shaped%20by%20his%20conversion%20to%20Islam%20in%201968%2C%20which%20is%20when%20he%20took%20the%20name%20Abdullah%20Ibrahim%2C%20and%20by%20his%20practice%20of%20martial%20arts%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fzenstudies.org%2Fteachings%2Fwhat-is-zen%2F%5C%22%3Ezen%3C%2Fa%3E%20(a%20form%20of%20Buddhism).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FkHG4Sjkso0Y%3Fwmode%3Dtransparent%26start%3D0%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20shaped%20musically%20by%20the%20variety%20of%20different%20musics%20he%20heard%20in%20Cape%20Town.%20These%20include%20jazz%2C%20the%20Cape%20carnival%20troupes%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.capetownmagazine.com%2Fkaapse-klopse%5C%22%3Eklopse%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20music%20of%20people%20who%20practised%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Ftopic%2FSufism%5C%22%3ESufi%3C%2Fa%3E%20branch%20of%20Islam%20in%20the%20Cape%20and%20whose%20chanting%2C%20drumming%20and%20dancing%20he%20witnessed.%20He%20was%20influenced%20by%20the%20Christian%20hymns%20played%20by%20his%20mother%20and%20other%20music%20he%20heard%20at%20the%20African%20Methodist%20Episcopal%20Church%2C%20which%20included%20gospel%20and%20African-American%20spirituals.%20He%20was%20shaped%20by%20jazz%20and%20dance%20band%20music%20and%20by%20African%20traditional%20music%20from%20Lesotho%2C%20the%20country%20of%20his%20father%3B%20even%20by%20Indian%20classical%20music%20and%20western%20art%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20distinguishes%20his%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20work%20as%20a%20composer%20is%20distinguished%20by%20its%20pianism%20and%20its%20international%20flavour%20with%20a%20strong%20dose%20of%20South%20Africa.%20He%20has%20also%20played%20flute%2C%20cello%20and%20soprano%20sax%20%E2%80%93%20which%20gave%20him%20insights%20into%20ensemble%20playing%20%E2%80%93%20but%20he%20is%20above%20all%20a%20brilliant%20pianist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20written%20great%20tunes%20but%20it%20is%20his%20harmonies%2C%20textures%2C%20colours%2C%20rhythms%2C%20phrasing%20and%20pianistic%20flow%20that%20make%20his%20compositions%20outstanding.%20His%20recordings%20are%20distinguished%20by%20the%20huge%20development%20of%20jazz%20style%20and%20treatment%20within%20them%20over%2070%20years.%20His%20music%20of%20the%201960s%20contains%20some%20really%20avant-garde%20(experimental)%20sounds%3B%20his%20music%20from%20the%201970s%20and%201980s%20is%20full%20of%20references%20to%20Africa%20in%20the%20titles%20of%20pieces%20and%20within%20the%20music%20itself.%20In%20the%201990s%2C%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sahistory.org.za%2Farticle%2Fsouth-africa-first-20-years-democracy-1994-2014%5C%22%3Efall%20of%20apartheid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ibrahim%E2%80%99s%20music%20took%20on%20a%20more%20sentimental%20mood.%20In%20later%20life%20he%20became%20more%20interested%20in%20arrangements%2C%20in%20orchestrating%20his%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20thing%20that%20distinguishes%20his%20career%20is%20that%20while%20he%20has%20always%20written%20new%20pieces%20he%20has%20also%20constantly%20reinvented%20and%20reimagined%20old%20ones%2C%20mainly%20through%20his%20own%20playing%20and%20often%20in%20his%20solo%20playing.%20It%20is%20as%20if%20he%20is%20remembering%20through%20his%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FpoYFln5s4e0%3Fwmode%3Dtransparent%26start%3D0%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F248952564_Abdullah_Ibrahim_and_the_Uses_of_Memory%23fullTextFileContent%5C%22%3EMemory%3C%2Fa%3E%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20all%20his%20music%3A%20he%20is%20always%20looking%20back%2C%20and%20sometimes%20he%20finds%20something%20there%20that%20helps%20us%20face%20the%20future.%20This%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20just%20apply%20to%20pieces%2C%20it%20applies%20to%20the%20way%20he%20plays.%20He%20could%20always%20be%20quite%20sparse%2C%20but%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years%20the%20pared-down%20simplicity%20of%20his%20playing%2C%20its%20clean%20lines%2C%20is%20more%20introspective%2C%20more%20philosophical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201970s%20and%201980s%20he%20was%20the%20darling%20of%20the%20anti-apartheid%20movement%20because%20of%20the%20promise%20of%20freedom%20in%20his%20music%20and%20his%20going%20into%20exile.%20The%20same%20music%20speaks%20now%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F370566418_%2527Echoes_From_Africa%2527_Abdullah_Ibrahim%2527s_Black_Sonic_Geography%23fullTextFileContent%5C%22%3Escattered%20hopes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20almost%20unbearably%20poignant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20hear%20this%20in%20his%20rendition%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dzh-IEEKADAI%5C%22%3EWedding%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20his%202021%20album%20Solotude.%20Listening%20to%20this%2C%20people%20of%20my%20generation%20remember%20those%20fierce%20solo%20performances%20he%20gave%20when%20this%20song%20first%20appeared%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20those%20huge%20build-ups%20on%20the%20keyboard%20that%20ended%20very%20loud%2C%20both%20hands%20playing%20rapid%20repeated%20chords%20(his%20trademark%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstudy.com%2Flearn%2Flesson%2Ftremolo-overview-effect.html%23%3A%257E%3Atext%3DLesson%2520Summary-%2CTremolo%2520is%2520a%2520music%2520performance%2520technique%2520in%2520which%2520a%2520performer%2Cof%2520one%2520or%2520two%2520notes.%5C%22%3Etremolo%3C%2Fa%3E).%20It%20sounded%20like%20a%20hymn%20to%20freedom.%20Now%2C%20when%20playing%20this%20same%20piece%20his%20hands%20trace%20notes%20sporadically%20and%20gently%20on%20the%20keyboard%2C%20like%20a%20ghost%2C%20with%20the%20tune%20in%20his%20right%20hand%20occasionally%20ahead%20of%20the%20change%20of%20chords%20in%20the%20left.%20Minimal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20his%20career%20highlights%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20album%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discogs.com%2Frelease%2F4722632-The-Jazz-Epistles-Jazz-Epistle-Verse-1%5C%22%3EJazz%20Epistle%20%E2%80%93%20Verse%201%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20made%20in%201960%20with%20Dollar%20Brand%2C%20Mackay%20Davashe%2C%20Hugh%20Masekela%2C%20Jonas%20Gwangwa%20and%20Kippie%20Moeketsi%2C%20a%20quintet%20of%20the%20foremost%20jazz%20musicians%20of%20the%20day%2C%20was%20among%20the%20first%20black%20jazz%20recordings%20in%20South%20Africa.%20It%20was%20also%20a%20milestone%20in%20the%20careers%20of%20all%20participants%2C%20several%20of%20whom%20went%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpure.royalholloway.ac.uk%2Fws%2Fportalfiles%2Fportal%2F26880662%2F2016vossphd.pdf%5C%22%3Einto%20exile%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDollar%20Brand%20and%20his%20wife%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fthe-marginalised-african-songbird-who-finally-became-visible-again-57448%5C%22%3ESathima%20Bea%20Benjamin%3C%2Fa%3E%20went%20into%20exile%20in%201962%2C%20at%20first%20in%20Zurich.%20While%20he%20was%20there%2C%20Duke%20Ellington%20heard%20him%20play%20in%201963%20and%20immediately%20produced%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.allmusic.com%2Falbum%2Fduke-ellington-presents-the-dollar-brand-trio-mw0000089493%5C%22%3Ealbum%3C%2Fa%3E%20Duke%20Ellington%20presents%20The%20Dollar%20Brand%20Trio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201965%20the%20couple%20moved%20to%20New%20York%2C%20which%20was%20their%20home%20for%20many%20years%20with%20only%20occasional%20trips%20back%20to%20South%20Africa.%20They%20founded%20their%20own%20record%20label%20in%201981%2C%20Ekapa%20(The%20Cape)%2C%20although%20he%20continued%20to%20record%20with%20the%20Enja%20label.%20Ekapa%20also%20became%20the%20name%20of%20the%20septet%20he%20formed%20in%201983.%20He%20composed%20music%20for%20the%20award-winnning%20film%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imdb.com%2Ftitle%2Ftt0094868%2F%5C%22%3EChocolat%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%201988.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FL5i4stj4M30%3Fwmode%3Dtransparent%26start%3D0%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201990%20he%20gave%20triumphant%20%E2%80%9Chomecoming%E2%80%9D%20concerts%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nelsonmandela.org%2Fbiography%5C%22%3ENelson%20Mandela%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20anti-apartheid%20activists%20were%20released%20from%20prison.%20In%20the%201990s%2C%20now%20spending%20part%20of%20his%20time%20abroad%20and%20part%20at%20home%2C%20Ibrahim%20began%20expanding%20his%20sound%20world%20into%20orchestral%20arrangements%20of%20his%20music%2C%20performing%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabdullahibrahim.co.za%2Frecord%2Fafrican-symphony%2F%5C%22%3EAfrican%20Symphony%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Munich%20in%202001.%20In%201994%20he%20performed%2C%20memorably%2C%20at%20Mandela%E2%80%99s%20presidential%20inauguration.%20There%20have%20been%20many%20other%20memorable%20concerts%20and%20awards%20in%20his%20recent%20career.%20His%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DL5i4stj4M30%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Chome%20concert%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20online%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20reveals%20his%20more%20intimate%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20it%20common%20to%20be%20performing%20at%2090%3F%20What%E2%80%99s%20his%20secret%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20professions%2C%20like%20conducting%2C%20yes.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20rare.%20Great%20pianists%20of%20the%20past%20played%20on%20into%20their%2090s%20but%20made%20more%20and%20more%20mistakes%20playing%20the%20same%20music%20the%20same%20way.%20Abdullah%20Ibrahim%20has%20pared%20down%20his%20playing%20as%20he%20has%20grown%20older%2C%20distilled%20it.%20Like%20well-matured%20brandy%2C%20you%20only%20need%20a%20sip%20and%20everything%20is%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20he%20could%20also%20be%20minimal%20in%20his%20youth%2C%20but%20now%20it%E2%80%99s%20for%20a%20different%20reason%2C%20because%20he%E2%80%99s%20in%20a%20very%20different%20space.%20He%20has%20become%20more%20and%20more%20zen.%20I%20imagine%20him%20as%20very%20disciplined%2C%20which%20I%20am%20sure%20has%20helped%20him%20maintain%20his%20health%20and%20strength%20as%20an%20artist.%20His%202024%20tour%20looks%20punishing%2C%20but%20he%20is%20taking%20plenty%20of%20breaks%20in%20between%20concerts%20in%20Italy%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20Germany%20and%20the%20US.%20Abdullah%20Ibrahim%20ends%20his%20world%20tour%20in%20Bavaria%2C%20where%20the%20final%20concerts%20are%20scheduled%20to%20be%20given%20immediately%20after%20he%20turns%2090%2C%20on%209%20October.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F225026%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Fchristine-lucia-1113281%5C%22%3EChristine%20Lucia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Extraordinary%20Professor%2C%20