2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Narendra%20Modi%20does%20not%20have%20a%20cordial%20relationship%20with%20those%20who%20disagree%20with%20him.%20Not%20too%20long%20ago%2C%20he%20called%20peaceful%20protestors%20%E2%80%98andolanjeevis%E2%80%99.%20He%20also%20called%20them%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eparjeevis%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(parasites)%20in%20the%20same%20breath.%20In%20Parliament%2C%20no%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eparjeevi%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20slur%2C%20one%20might%20recall%2C%20was%20hurled%20at%20those%20who%20most%20certainly%20did%20not%20deserve%20it%20%E2%80%94%20farmers%20who%20feed%20the%20nation%2C%20and%20who%20were%20compelled%C2%A0%20to%20spend%20more%20than%20a%20year%20at%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20borders%20protesting%20against%20farm%20bills%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20ultimately%20had%20to%20rescind.%20The%20farmers%20didn%E2%80%99t%20mind%20being%20called%20%E2%80%98andolanjeevis%E2%80%99%20but%20took%20strong%20exception%20to%20being%20labelled%20%E2%80%98parasites%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20and%20a%20half%20years%20later%2C%20they%20have%20now%20stopped%20expecting%20any%20kindness%20or%20fairness%20from%20the%20government%20in%20power.%C2%A0The%20%3Cem%3EKisan%20Mahapanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20organised%20by%20the%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%20at%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20historical%20Ram%20Lila%20grounds%20on%20March%2014%20underscored%20that%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20then%2C%20why%20protest%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20A.R.%20Sindhu%20from%20the%20Centre%20for%20Indian%20Trade%20Unions%20(CITU)%20that%20has%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20SKM%2C%20explained%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20here%20to%20convince%20this%20government%20to%20mend%20its%20ways.%20We%20know%20it%20won%E2%80%99t.%20This%20government%20only%20listens%20to%20its%20corporate%20friends%20and%20is%20deaf%20and%20blind%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20farmers%20and%20workers.%20We%20are%20here%2C%20instead%2C%20to%20send%20a%20clear%20and%20ringing%20message%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20that%20resistance%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%5BBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%5D%20ideology%20and%20policies%20is%20alive%20and%20well%2C%20and%20that%20we%20will%20not%20quit%20till%20we%20receive%20justice.%20We%20are%20here%20to%20wake%20people%20up!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20sort%20of%20sadness%2C%20however%2C%20hung%20in%20the%20air%20at%20the%20well-attended%20event.%20But%20this%20was%20not%20the%20despondency%20of%20those%20who%20have%20given%20up%20and%20conceded%20defeat.%20This%20was%20the%20sadness%20of%20those%20who%20have%20been%20continually%20ignored%2C%20exploited%2C%20lied%20to%2C%20and%20vilified%2C%20but%20who%20have%20decided%20to%20continue%20to%20fight%20against%20great%20odds%2C%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMixed%20with%20the%20sadness%20was%20anger.%20If%20one%20might%20use%20the%20metaphor%20of%20the%20roadside%20%3Cem%3Echaiwallah%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20tea%2C%20this%20was%20not%20the%20kind%20of%20fresh%20anger%20that%20suddenly%20sizzles%20and%20boils%20over%2C%20but%20the%20sort%20that%20has%20been%20simmering%20on%20a%20low%20flame%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20the%20kind%20that%20can%20scald%2C%20if%20the%20tea%20drinker%20is%20not%20careful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fthe-solution-to-farmers-problems-lies-in-the-macro%5C%22%3EThe%20Solution%20to%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Problems%20Lies%20in%20the%20Macro%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%20personnel%2C%20M.%20Chaturvedi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20served%20my%20country%20for%2031%20years%20with%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force.%20Today%20I%20am%20standing%20with%20our%20farmers.%20We%20are%20the%20children%20of%20farmers%2C%20and%20fathers%20and%20sons%2C%20both%2C%20are%20unhappy.%20The%20sons%20guarding%20the%20borders%20have%20lost%20their%20pensions%20and%20the%20promise%20of%20a%20stable%20life%20because%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EAgniveer%20Yojana%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20their%20fathers%20are%20unhappy%20because%20they%20are%20not%20getting%20fair%20price%20for%20their%20produce!%20How%20will%20the%20sons%20and%20daughters%20of%20farmers%20guarding%20the%20borders%20be%20happy%20when%20their%20parents%20are%20in%20distress%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Dr.%20Ashish%20Mital%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sabha%20(AIKMS)%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20government%20has%20betrayed%20and%20cheated%20the%20farmers.%20With%20this%20%3Cem%3Emahapanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20we%20are%20once%20again%20reiterating%20our%20demands%20for%20MSP%2C%20loan%20waivers%2C%20and%20justice%20for%20those%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20Lakhimpur%20Khiri.%20There%20can%20be%20no%20real%20%E2%80%98development%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20country%20till%20the%20very%20real%20issues%20of%20the%20farmers%20are%20addressed.%20We%20also%20want%20to%20send%20out%20the%20message%20that%20the%20farmers%20of%20the%20country%20are%20not%20divided%2C%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20wage%20peaceful%20protest%20till%20we%20win.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20571px)%2085vw%2C%20571px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F15170408%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-15-at-5.03.41-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22571%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F15170408%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-15-at-5.03.41-PM.png%20571w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F15170408%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-15-at-5.03.41-PM-300x241.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701828%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22458%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20farmer%20at%20the%20Mahapanchayat.%20Photo%3A%20Rohit%20Kumar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20been%20to%20more%20democratic%20protests%20these%20past%20ten%20years%20than%20I%20can%20count%2C%20but%20there%20was%20something%20particularly%20heart-breaking%20about%20this%20particular%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20it%20was%20the%20sight%20of%20thousands%20of%20elderly%20and%20visibly%20poor%20farmers%20in%20old%20and%20worn%20clothes%20who%20really%20should%20not%20have%20had%20to%20sit%20on%20the%20rocky%2C%20dusty%2C%20uneven%20ground%20of%20Ramlila%20Maidan.%20Or%20maybe%20it%20was%20the%20sight%20of%20elderly%20women%20farmers%20sitting%20in%20the%20sun%20holding%20their%20farmer%20union%20flags%2C%20listening%20to%20the%20speeches%20of%20their%20leaders%2C%20and%20sharing%20little%20%3Cem%3Epotlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(bags)%20of%20food%20with%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOr%20perhaps%20it%20was%20the%20grim%20fact%20that%2C%20on%20an%20average%2C%20154%20farmers%20and%20daily%20wagers%2C%20very%20much%20like%20the%20ones%20present%20at%20Ramlila%20Maidan%2C%20die%20by%20suicide%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20approach%20roads%20to%20the%20ground%20are%20dotted%20with%20billboards%20and%20hoardings%20proclaiming%20%E2%80%9CModi%20%3Cem%3Eki%3C%2Fem%3E%20guarantee%20%5BModi%E2%80%99s%20gurantee%5D%E2%80%9D.%20The%20sight%20of%20farmers%20walking%20beneath%20them%20seemed%20like%20a%20cruel%20joke.%20As%20an%20attending%20protestor%20put%20it%20wryly%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20used%20to%20call%20them%20%3Cem%3Ejumlas%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebut%20then%20%3Cem%3Ejumla%3C%2Fem%3E%20became%20a%20bad%20word.%20Now%20they%20call%20them%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98guarantees%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalking%20amongst%20the%20farmers%2C%20I%20wished%20I%20could%20have%20brought%20along%20a%20busload%20of%20high%20school%20students%20that%20I%20do%20workshops%20for%2C%20on%20topics%20like%20empathy%20and%20care.%20There%E2%80%99s%20nothing%20quite%20like%20a%20field%20trip%20to%20understand%20suffering%20and%20solidarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20I%20would%20have%20liked%20to%20bring%20school%20students%20along%20was%20to%20give%20them%20an%20opportunity%20to%20learn%20directly%20from%20the%20farmers%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20excellent%20teachers%20and%20have%20the%20gift%20of%20being%20able%20to%20explain%20complex%20things%20simply%20and%20clearly%2C%20as%20did%20Baljinder%20Singh%20Mann%2C%20a%20Bhartiya%20Kisan%20Union%20leader%20from%20the%20Terai%20region%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHolding%20a%20small%20packet%20of%20potato%20chips%2C%20he%20explained%20to%20me%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20packet%20of%20chips%20cost%20Rs%205.%20It%20contains%20barely%2010%20grams%20of%20potato%20wafers.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20packet%20contains%20air.%20The%20farmer%20who%20grew%20the%20potatoes%20that%20the%20manufacturer%20used%2C%20was%20paid%20barely%20two%20to%20three%20rupees%20per%20kilo.%20The%20merchant%20made%20Rs%20500%20off%20that%20kilo%20of%20potatoes%2C%20but%20the%20farmer%20who%20worked%20for%20six%20months%20to%20grow%20that%20kilo%20of%20potatoes%20got%20only%20two%20or%20three%20rupees%20for%20his%20efforts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-protest-should-turn-the-spotlight-on-indias-impending-water-crisis%5C%22%3EFarmers%20Protest%20Should%20Turn%20the%20Spotlight%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20Impending%20Water%20Crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20you%20consumers%20to%20understand%20that%20we%20are%20fighting%20YOUR%20battle!%20We%20are%20trying%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20grains%20that%20feed%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20go%20into%20the%20pockets%20of%20the%20corporates.%20As%20long%20as%20the%20crops%20and%20grains%20come%20to%20you%20from%20the%20house%20of%20the%20farmer%2C%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20them.%20The%20moment%20farming%20passes%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20corporates%2C%20they%20will%20then%20charge%20whatever%20they%20want%20and%20your%20daily%20food%20will%20meet%20the%20same%20fate%20as%20this%20packet%20of%20chips%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20know%20the%20students%20would%20have%20enjoyed%20meeting%20Baljinder%20Mann%20and%20learning%20from%20him.%20But%20I%20also%20know%20that%20very%20few%20urban%20parents%20would%20have%20allowed%20their%20children%20to%20go%20on%20such%20an%20expedition%2C%20so%20insular%20and%20fearful%20have%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20made%20them.%20Very%20few%20high%20school%20teenagers%20are%20like%20Mallika%2C%20whose%20parents%20did%20not%20stop%20her%20from%20visiting%20the%20farmers%20at%20Ghazipur%20border%20regularly%20during%20the%202020-21%20Delhi%20%3Cem%3Eandolan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(protests).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20met%20Mallika%20and%20her%20classmates%20%E2%80%94%20all%20class%2012%20students%20%E2%80%94%20at%20Ghazipur.%20They%20were%20holding%20up%20a%20poster%20that%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Zulmi%20jab%20jab%20zulm%20karega%20satta%20ke%20galiyaaron%20se%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EChappa%20chappa%20goonj%20uthega%20inquilab%20ke%20naaron%20s%3C%2Fem%3Ee%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoughly%20translated%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20cruelty%20and%20oppression%20spill%20out%20of%20the%20corridors%20of%20powers%2C%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20land%20will%20echo%20with%20cries%20of%20revolution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%E2%80%99%20ongoing%20struggle%20has%20certainly%20borne%20out%20the%20truth%20of%20those%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERohit%20Kumar%20is%20an%20educator%2C%20author%2C%20and%20independent%20journalist%2C%20and%20can%20be%20reached%20at%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aletsempathize%40gmail.com%5C%22%3Eletsempathize%40gmail.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710504050000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F15170218%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-15-at-5.01