2%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F121371%2Fanahad-tribal-music%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etribal%20musicians%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20across%20the%20country%20composed%20and%20launched%20five%20original%20compositions%20on%20a%20tribal%20narrative%20at%20the%20conclave.%20The%20compositions%20are%20on%20the%20theme%20of%20unifying%20tribals%20in%20the%20face%20of%20adversity.%20They%20include%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ENukhtharini%20Juwmang%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Rabha%20tribe%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EEklaivet%20Ajakong%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Karbi%20tribe%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EDela%20Dela%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Santal%20tribe%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EAbua%20Disom%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20Ho%20tribe%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20significant%20outcome%20of%20Samvaad%E2%80%99s%20ten-year%20journey%20was%20seen%20in%20Jaincy%20John%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20to%20break%20away%20from%20the%20conventional%20narrative%20of%20urban%20education.%20Living%20in%20cities%20often%20limits%20our%20view%20of%20education%20to%20securing%20future%20jobs.%20However%2C%20for%20those%20in%20remote%20areas%20far%20from%20mainstream%20society%2C%20education%20is%20about%20identity%20and%20challenging%20stereotypes%20built%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20academician%20and%20activist%20from%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Mala%20Arya%20community%2C%20Jaincy%20challenged%20the%20stereotypes%20around%20tribal%20identity.%20While%20she%20was%20working%20on%20extensive%20pieces%20on%20Adivasi%20and%20Dalit%20art%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20history%2C%20and%20completing%20her%20PhD%2C%20she%20encountered%20discrimination%20and%20abuse%20from%20her%20guide.%20However%2C%20that%20did%20not%20deter%20her%20from%20her%20path.%20She%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20him%2C%20which%20further%20helped%20other%20women%20open%20up%20about%20their%20similar%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Jancy%20continues%20to%20fight%20the%20legal%20battle%2C%20Samvaad%20has%20supported%20the%20right%20of%20many%20tribal%20members%20to%20represent%20themselves%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F212493%2Ftata-steel-india-tribe-conclave-samvaad-jamshedpur-jharkhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENothing%20about%20us%20without%20us%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20important%20because%20tribal%20individuals%20deserve%20recognition%20as%20prominent%20leaders%2C%20and%20Samvaad%20is%20dedicated%20to%20amplifying%20their%20visibility.%20The%20conclave%20advocates%20for%20inclusivity%20and%20equality%2C%20ensuring%20that%20everyone%20has%20a%20voice%20and%20uniting%20those%20who%20have%20faced%20exploitation%20due%20to%20their%20identity.%20Today%2C%20members%20of%20tribal%20communities%20are%20not%20simply%20demanding%20a%20seat%20at%20the%20table%3B%20they%20are%20actively%20forging%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%3A%20Samvaad%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710164862000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-scaled.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344526%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tata%20Samvaad%2C%20enabled%20by%20the%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20brings%20together%20200%20tribal%20communities%20annually%20to%20celebrate%20their%20rich%20culture%20and%20identity%20through%20art%2C%20food%2C%20workshops%2C%20and%20conversations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Gopi%20Karelia%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344526%2Fsamvaad-tata-steel-foundation-celebrates-culture-of-tribes-of-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IFS%20Officer%20S