0scuba%20diver%20has%20given%20me%20an%20immense%20sense%20of%20responsibility.%20The%20oceans%20do%20not%20have%20a%20voice.%20I%20am%20one%20of%20the%20few%20who%20could%20communicate%20the%20reality.%20My%20work%20is%20small%20and%20it%20will%20take%20an%20entire%20village%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20change.%20We%20do%20not%20just%20need%20to%20talk%20the%20talk%20but%20walk%20the%20walk%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Uma%20Mani)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709736705000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fcoral-woman-1-1709730480.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344098%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tamil%20Nadu-based%20Uma%20Mani%20turned%20to%20deep-sea%20scuba%20diving%20at%20the%20age%20of%2049.%20Today%2C%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20she%20has%20made%20it%20her%20life%E2%80%99s%20mission%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20marine%20pollution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344098%2Fuma-mani-scuba-diver-senior-citizen-painter-raises-awareness-on-rising-marine-pollution-coral-reefs%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Couldn%E2%80%99t%20Dream%20Earlier%20So%20I%20Started%20at%2037%E2%80%99%3A%20Woman%E2%80%99s%20Startup%20Uses%20Flowers%20to%20Make%20Rs%202%20Lakh%2FMonth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20children%20went%20to%20college%2C%20Poonam%20Singh%20felt%20an%20overwhelming%20sense%20of%20loneliness.%20Married%20at%2018%2C%20the%20Gurgaon%20resident%20faced%20the%20proverbial%20%E2%80%98Empty%20Nest%20Syndrome%E2%80%99.%20She%20had%20many%20dreams%2C%20but%20most%20remained%20unfulfilled%20as%20she%20remained%20tied%20in%20the%20intricacies%20of%20everyday%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlone%2C%20depressed%20and%20in%20search%20of%20her%20identity%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330948%2Fp-bindu-organic-farmer-tamil-nadu-innovation-msme-kvk-agriculture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20mother%3C%2Fa%3E%20advised%20her%20to%20visit%20a%20temple.%20Looking%20for%20solace%2C%20she%20headed%20to%20a%20nearby%20temple%20and%20offered%20some%20flowers%20to%20the%20deity.%20What%20happened%20next%20shocked%20her.%20The%20flowers%20were%20thrown%20into%20a%20garbage%20bin%20without%20even%20being%20kept%20at%20the%20deity%E2%80%99s%20feet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20sat%20at%20the%20temple%20for%20a%20while%2C%20she%20noticed%20that%20all%20flowers%20faced%20the%20same%20fate.%20Disturbed%20by%20this%2C%20the%20then%2037-year-old%20returned%20home%20and%20researched%20about%20what%20happens%20to%20flower%20waste%20at%20temples.%20An%20International%20Journal%20for%20Research%20in%20Applied%20Science%20%26amp%3B%20Engineering%20Technology%20report%20states%20that%20every%20year%2C%20approximately%20eight%20million%20tonnes%20of%20waste%20flowers%20are%20dumped%20in%C2%A0Indian%20rivers.%20Poonam%20adds%20that%20floral%20waste%20reportedly%20accounts%20for%2016%20percent%20of%20the%20river%20pollutants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonam%20had%20found%20her%20calling%20and%20set%20out%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20floral%20waste.%20In%20June%202019%2C%20she%20set%20up%20Aaruhi%20Enterprises%20with%20her%20friend%20Pinki%20Yadav%2C%20and%20started%20making%20incense%20sticks%2C%20dhoop%20sticks%2C%20diyas%2C%20idols%20and%20more%2C%20using%20floral%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20month%2C%20her%20venture%20recycles%201%2C000%20kg%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339831%2Fjamshedpur-rajiv-sharma-alve-smart-air-fresheners-plastic-free-eco-friendly-temple-flower-waste%2F%5C%22%20targe