20challenge%20of%20hairfall.%20The%20duo%20made%20the%20oil%20together%2C%20which%20took%20an%20entire%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20faced%20tremendous%20hair%20fall.%20After%20using%20it%20for%20about%20two-three%20months%2C%20we%20found%20that%20our%20hairfall%20had%20greatly%20reduced%20and%20our%20hair%20was%20growing.%20I%20started%20making%20it%20for%20my%20daughter%20and%20our%20domestic%20help%2C%20who%20also%20found%20it%20greatly%20effective%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rajni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20Tuteja-Dua%20family%20shifted%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Gurugram%2C%20into%20an%20apartment%20complex.%20It%20was%20here%20that%20Nidhi%20would%20find%20an%20opportunity%20to%20give%20shape%20to%20her%20desires.%20She%20found%20women%20here%20who%20were%20running%20small%20businesses%20from%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20mothers%2C%20Nidhi%2C%20too%2C%20had%20a%20burning%20desire%20to%20have%20a%20flourishing%20career.%20When%20she%20heard%20about%20these%20women%2C%20she%20found%20her%20window.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20thought%20that%20I%20would%20join%20the%20office%20again.%20I%20missed%20my%20financial%20freedom%20and%20kept%20thinking%20of%20what%20I%20could%20do%20to%20reclaim%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nidhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajni%2C%20who%20had%20spent%20her%20life%20taking%20care%20of%20her%20children%2C%20followed%20by%20her%20grandchildren%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20harbour%20such%20aspirations%2C%20she%20shares.%20But%20when%20Nidhi%20asked%20for%20her%20help%2C%20the%20indulgent%20mother-in-law%2C%20went%20all%20in%20to%20support%20her%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20started%20distributing%20the%20oil%20to%20women%20in%20our%20society.%20To%20our%20surprise%2C%20they%20kept%20coming%20back%20for%20more.%20In%20fact%2C%20our%20doorbell%20used%20to%20keep%20ringing%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20Nidhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20they%20would%20pack%20the%20oil%20in%20normal%20bottles%20with%20a%20sticker.%20The%20first%20batch%20of%20one%20litre%20was%20made%20on%20a%20small%20kadhai%20and%20sold%2010%20bottles.%20As%20soon%20as%20Nidhi%20posted%20on%20a%20Whatsapp%20group%2C%20they%20were%20sold%20out%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20925px)%20100vw%2C%20925px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22925%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nidhi%20and%20Rajni%20started%20making%20the%20hair%20oil%20for%20their%20own%20use%20in%202020%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491.jpeg%20925w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491-234x300.jpeg%20234w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491-500x641.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491-768x985.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491-150x192.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343999%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221186%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENidhi%20and%20Rajni%20started%20making%20the%20hair%20oil%20for%20their%20own%20use%20in%202020%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20they%20had%20given%20their%20oil%20to%20over%20200%20people%20in%20the%20society%2C%20the%20software%20engineer%20realised%20the%20viability%20of%20her%20business.%20As%20orders%20increased%2C%20they%20bought%20bigger%20vessels%2C%20a%20five%20litre%20and%2010%20litre%20kadhai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202023%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20increase%20their%20presence%20and%20set%20up%20an%20Instagram%20account%2C%20%E2%80%98Nidhi%E2%80%99s%20Grandmaa%20Secret%E2%